    <node id="&quot;WUHAN'S LOCKDOWN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan's Lockdown was a significant measure taken to contain the viral outbreak, restricting movement in and out of the city."</data>
