    <node id="&quot;HUAZHONG UNIVERSITY OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">Huazhong University of Science and Technology is an educational institution known for its specialization in electrical engineering, from which Liu Xuerong graduated. The university has also been affected by the recent outbreak of a virus, having lost a professor to its impacts, highlighting the widespread effects of the situation on the academic community.</data>
