    <node id="&quot;TONGJI HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">Tongji Hospital is a medical facility located in Wuhan, China, and is affiliated with Huazhong University of Science and Technology. It is recognized for its expertise in organ transplantation. During the outbreak of the coronavirus, Tongji Hospital played a significant role in the healthcare system, being one of the three hospitals in Wuhan that accepted non-novel coronavirus patients. However, it has also been reported that the hospital is hesitant to officially report new coronavirus cases, indicating a level of concern regarding the transparency of its reporting during the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,05facbc17efc22acf453283e5f155f6b,06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,0ea87bb3f7f4f08e19bd21127da9be59,0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d,107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,1a74ad918264f9c92231f7eea81aa970,1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,2014d81b9f4aeb008dab606a9f719b7a,203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2,24f82cd50519ba6e59f128ccf5c821f6,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,2c5e9cdd8d1ed971c72785d384814175,2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,39d6ae4d79ba80953eb86122bce3240d,3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a,3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf,527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,54353bad2befd9d61191dd25ba0263f5,548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b,5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637,5a58a4c5bcc46fb9d4065918796e6b69,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5,603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6,6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a