    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE VIRAL OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">"The Viral Outbreak" refers to the health crisis affecting Wuhan and Hubei, which has prompted significant medical and community responses.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,05facbc17efc22acf453283e5f155f6b,06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,0ea87bb3f7f4f08e19bd21127da9be59,0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d,107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,1a74ad918264f9c92231f7eea81aa970,1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,2014d81b9f4aeb008dab606a9f719b7a,203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2,24f82cd50519ba6e59f128ccf5c821f6,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,2c5e9cdd8d1ed971c72785d384814175,2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,39d6ae4d79ba80953eb86122bce3240d,3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a,3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf,527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,54353bad2befd9d61191dd25ba0263f5,548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b,5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637,5a58a4c5bcc46fb9d4065918796e6b69,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5,603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6,6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a,68d1018c902661392b4e20435e4961ad,70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa,70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,8119bda66f27343b4be177610dcff2af,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b,8127e2d84213dc7f69446ae542408f8b,81ac5d9d3486351095e7556baea13868,82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6,8475b5acce1676914c613935d50901d6,88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab,8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f,8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,941fd97efac4d3db43e927529ff925c4,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae,9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b,96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff,973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb,a1228c3edf57aa00b38f80de4ec91c5e,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47,a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1,a45ab7ca6e1942a4732b13ef47f6587f,a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df,a784bfe671571202f52c5445629f1862,ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435,ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,b311864054a222e4315c575af55fca03,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748,c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12,c45145c12a7fedd7064529e344fa3e04,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95,d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c,db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39,e27a49f034d2f2f425ddd0e46dee9822,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062,e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412,e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf,ecdbc80cd38edf6145de3f6de4c35bb9,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944,ee747c2b3ef4b0d990341dab895eb81d,f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185,f7d4aedaaebf83b5bb28320eecdc7d6c,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947,f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e,fd7d025a46189bb316ef893020b7e22d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SINGAPORE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Singapore is a city-state located in Southeast Asia. Currently, arrangements are being made for citizens to return amidst a quarantine situation. The country has a diverse population, and it is noted that the niece of the narrator has lived in Singapore for over a decade, identifying as Singaporean-Chinese.</data>
      <data key="d2">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SHANGHAI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Shanghai is a major city in China known for its significant role during the coronavirus outbreak. Dr. Zhang Wenhong, a prominent figure in the city, is recognized for his effective guidance throughout the health crisis. The economic impact of the pandemic is also evident in Shanghai, as illustrated by an incident where a man experienced price inflation for face masks. Additionally, the city has seen various health-related incidents, including a case where an individual was hospitalized but later determined to have a common cold rather than a serious illness. Overall, Shanghai has been a focal point for both health and economic challenges during the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6,ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf,ee747c2b3ef4b0d990341dab895eb81d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE NEW YEAR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">Chinese New Year is a significant cultural event that holds great importance in China. It is a time for celebration and family gatherings; however, recent challenges have impacted these traditions. The ongoing coronavirus outbreak coincided with the holiday, leading to health challenges for some individuals and complicating travel and activities due to quarantine measures. Families have found it difficult to come together and celebrate as they normally would, as the outbreak has affected social activities and the availability of caregivers for the elderly. Despite these challenges, the spirit of the holiday remains, with well-wishes being extended to everyone during this time.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb,ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748,d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95,ecdbc80cd38edf6145de3f6de4c35bb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIAO LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiao Li is a colleague who informed the narrator about the infection of two individuals from the same family living nearby."</data>
      <data key="d2">ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE INFECTED COUPLE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Infected Couple refers to two individuals from the same family who have contracted the coronavirus and are self-quarantining."</data>
      <data key="d2">ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE EX-HUSBAND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Ex-Husband is mentioned as having been hospitalized in Shanghai but is later confirmed to have a common cold and not the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DAUGHTER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Daughter" is a character who plays a significant role in a narrative centered around a family navigating the challenges of a lockdown. She is depicted as the narrator's child, who shares a dinner with her father, the ex-husband, illustrating the complexities of family dynamics during the quarantine. The Daughter's experiences and feelings are central to the story, reflecting the personal concerns and emotional impact that the crisis has on her and her family.</data>
      <data key="d2">527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Government Officials are representatives from Hubei who held a press conference about the coronavirus outbreak, facing public scrutiny."</data>
      <data key="d2">ad43e1b0afe90e62a3b11cf82cc601cf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;N95 MASKS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
      <data key="d1">N95 masks are protective face masks that have become increasingly important during health crises, particularly due to their effectiveness in stopping the spread of viruses. These masks are currently in high demand, leading to challenges related to their availability and pricing. As a result, N95 masks play a crucial role in public health efforts to mitigate the transmission of infectious diseases.</data>
      <data key="d2">527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,ee747c2b3ef4b0d990341dab895eb81d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XU MIN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Xu Min is an old classmate of the narrator who played a significant role during a visit to Chengdu by providing an N95 mask to help protect against poor air quality. This gesture was particularly valuable as the mask later proved useful during a health crisis, highlighting Xu Min's thoughtfulness and consideration for the narrator's well-being in challenging circumstances.</data>
      <data key="d2">3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,ee747c2b3ef4b0d990341dab895eb81d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE NARRATOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Narrator is a concerned individual residing in Wuhan, who is deeply affected by the impact of the virus on families in the region. They advocate for accountability among officials in response to the crisis. As a resident of Wuhan, The Narrator faces the challenges of obtaining face masks during this health emergency while also managing the responsibilities of caring for a pet. Additionally, The Narrator reflects on their past experiences during the Cultural Revolution and the subsequent Reform Era, offering insights into the importance of education and the value of independent thought. Through these reflections, The Narrator provides a multifaceted perspective on the current health crisis, intertwined with personal history and social commentary.</data>
      <data key="d2">8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39,ee747c2b3ef4b0d990341dab895eb81d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIA CHUNPING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Xia Chunping is a deputy chief editor and assistant editor at the China News Agency. She is an old schoolmate of the narrator and played a significant role during the lockdown by providing masks and other supplies to the narrator during their quarantine. Her contributions included conducting an interview and ensuring that essential resources were delivered, highlighting her commitment to supporting others during challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OLD GENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Old Geng is a former classmate of the narrator who interacts with him during the lockdown and shares a mutual history with Xia Chunping."</data>
      <data key="d2">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIAO YUAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiao Yuan is an old friend of the narrator who delivered masks to him, showing support during the scarcity of supplies."</data>
      <data key="d2">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE VIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Virus refers to the coronavirus outbreak that originated in Wuhan, leading to significant changes in daily life and widespread lockdowns. This infectious disease has resulted in a high number of illnesses and fatalities, profoundly impacting families and straining the healthcare system. The outbreak prompted the quarantine of Wuhan, which not only caused widespread fear and disruption within the community but also led to shortages of essential supplies, such as face masks. Overall, The Virus has had a far-reaching effect on the lives of individuals and the functioning of communities.</data>
      <data key="d2">a1228c3edf57aa00b38f80de4ec91c5e,a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE LOCKDOWN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Lockdown" refers to a series of measures implemented in Wuhan to control the spread of the coronavirus, significantly impacting the daily lives of its residents. This period of restricted movement and activities lasted for over 20 days and was aimed at mitigating a health crisis. The Lockdown altered daily routines and interactions among citizens, as strict quarantine measures were enforced to limit the virus's transmission. Overall, The Lockdown represents a critical event in Wuhan's response to the pandemic, profoundly affecting the community's way of life during this challenging time.</data>
      <data key="d2">527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b,a1228c3edf57aa00b38f80de4ec91c5e,a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE LITERARY AND ARTS FEDERATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Literary and Arts Federation is a building where the narrator meets Xia Chunping and engages in discussions during the lockdown."</data>
      <data key="d2">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHINA NEWS AGENCY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The China News Agency is the media organization where Xia Chunping works, involved in reporting during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MAYOR ZHOU XIANWANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mayor Zhou Xianwang is the mayor of Wuhan, actively leading the city's response to the coronavirus outbreak, and is portrayed as a disciplined and pragmatic individual."</data>
      <data key="d2">23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PREMIER LI KEQIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Premier Li Keqiang is a high-ranking government official in China, mentioned in relation to the response to the outbreak and the actions of Mayor Zhou."</data>
      <data key="d2">23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Outbreak" refers to the coronavirus crisis that originated in Wuhan and has since evolved into a global pandemic. This health crisis has significantly impacted healthcare systems, public health responses, and daily life in Wuhan and the surrounding Hubei Province. Characterized by high infection rates and substantial mortality, the outbreak has led to widespread suffering and psychological trauma among the community.

The situation has prompted extensive public health measures, including lockdowns and quarantine protocols, which have drastically altered the lives of residents. The outbreak has not only affected physical health but has also resulted in significant social implications, leading to community responses and personal reflections on the crisis. As the viral epidemic continues to unfold, it has generated considerable public discourse and concern, highlighting the ongoing challenges faced by the region and the broader implications for global health.</data>
      <data key="d2">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b,8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df,a784bfe671571202f52c5445629f1862,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748,caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;40,000-PERSON PUBLIC BANQUET&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The 40,000-person public banquet is a large-scale community gathering in Wuhan that has been criticized for occurring during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE JOURNAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Journal is a publication that is being discussed in terms of whether to send out manuscripts for its next issue, indicating ongoing work despite the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;EAST RIVER GARDEN LANE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">East River Garden Lane is a location in Wuhan that has been associated with biking activities. It is a popular destination for bike rides; however, it is currently described as deserted due to the ongoing quarantine and the circumstances surrounding the outbreak. The narrator reflects on past experiences of biking in this area, highlighting the stark contrast between its former vibrancy and its present emptiness.</data>
      <data key="d2">9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUOSHENSHAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Huoshenshan Hospital is a newly constructed Level One medical facility located in Wuhan, specifically designed to isolate and treat critical patients during the coronavirus outbreak. Established as a temporary hospital, it was built rapidly to address the urgent medical needs arising from the health crisis. The hospital is noted for its good treatment facilities and aims to improve the conditions for patient care. As one of the key facilities treating critically ill patients during the early stages of the outbreak, Huoshenshan Hospital symbolizes the urgent healthcare response in Wuhan, providing essential medical support during this challenging time.</data>
      <data key="d2">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROFESSOR LIU CHUAN&#8217;E&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Professor Liu Chuan&#8217;e is a faculty member at Hubei University who expresses deep emotional distress over the current humanitarian crisis caused by the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JIANG ZIDAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Jiang Zidan is a specialist in traditional Chinese medicine who provides health advice to the narrator regarding their bronchitis condition."</data>
      <data key="d2">e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN UNIVERSITY CHINESE DEPARTMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan University Chinese Department is an academic institution where the author studied, indicating their educational background."</data>
      <data key="d2">9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "Coronavirus Outbreak" refers to the global health crisis that began in late 2019 in Wuhan, China. This outbreak has led to widespread illness and significant public health measures aimed at containing the virus. The crisis has resulted in high infection rates and mortality, prompting governmental responses, including lockdowns in Hubei Province. The outbreak has not only affected the health of individuals but has also had profound social impacts, altering daily life and healthcare practices for people in Wuhan and beyond. It has sparked widespread concern and discussions regarding its political and social implications, as well as challenges in managing patient care. Overall, the Coronavirus Outbreak represents a significant public health crisis with far-reaching effects on communities and healthcare systems globally.</data>
      <data key="d2">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf,73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b,973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LOTUS FLU CAPSULES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Lotus Flu Capsules are a medicinal product that the author uses as part of their regimen to combat illness during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MANTRA OF THE CLOSED DOOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The mantra of the closed door is a traditional chant taught to the author, symbolizing cultural practices aimed at health and protection."</data>
      <data key="d2">9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE GOVERNMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Government is a body that plays a crucial role in addressing public safety and order, particularly in the context of health crises such as the coronavirus outbreak. It is responsible for implementing a range of policies aimed at managing the outbreak, which includes tracking and investigation efforts in Wuhan, as well as managing quarantine procedures and hospital resource allocation. The Government has also made arrangements for the care of children orphaned by the pandemic and has committed to supporting vulnerable populations during this health crisis.

In addition to these responsibilities, the Government encompasses both central and local authorities in China, particularly those in Hubei and Wuhan, who are actively involved in responding to the outbreak. These authorities are tasked with implementing public health measures, managing the health crisis response, and addressing public concerns through leadership changes and new strategies. Overall, the Government's multifaceted approach aims to ensure public safety and effectively manage the challenges posed by the coronavirus outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d2">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a,527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae,9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;AUTHOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1" />
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HONGSHAN DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Hongshan Department of Transportation is responsible for facilitating transportation in Wuhan, particularly during the quarantine period."</data>
      <data key="d2">679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OFFICER XIAO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Officer Xiao is a police officer who assisted in getting a family member to the airport during the quarantine, demonstrating community support."</data>
      <data key="d2">679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Coronavirus refers to a global pandemic that originated in Wuhan, China, and has led to widespread health crises, significant changes in daily life, and extensive public health measures. This viral outbreak has particularly affected Hubei province, where it prompted quarantine measures and significant disruptions to daily activities and healthcare systems. The pandemic has resulted in numerous infections and deaths, impacting the lives of many individuals, including residents of Wuhan and beyond.

As the outbreak unfolded, it caused widespread fear and concern, leading to lockdowns and changes in medical practices. The Coronavirus has been associated with high mortality rates and has necessitated extensive management efforts by healthcare professionals and institutions. The pandemic has not only posed health challenges but has also resulted in significant social and economic issues, prompting discussions about responsibility and response to the crisis.

Overall, the Coronavirus has had a profound impact on communities worldwide, leading to a reevaluation of public health responses and the implementation of measures aimed at controlling the spread of the virus.</data>
      <data key="d2">16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a,82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae,9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7,ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39,e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE YOUNG MAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Young Man" is a character who experienced initial fear regarding the possibility of having contracted the coronavirus. This anxiety was prevalent as he worried about his health and the implications of the virus. However, he later received confirmation that he was not infected, which allowed him to reassure others about his well-being. His experience reflects the broader concerns and anxieties that many faced during the pandemic, highlighting the emotional impact of the virus on individuals.</data>
      <data key="d2">679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI WRITERS ASSOCIATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Hubei Writers Association is a prominent cultural and literary organization based in Hubei, China, dedicated to supporting writers and fostering literary expression. The association emphasizes social responsibility, particularly during crises such as the recent pandemic, where it has actively checked on the well-being of its members and engaged in community support initiatives. 

Historically, the association has played a significant role in the literary landscape of the region, with notable figures such as Fang Fang, who served as chair and was influential in shaping the organization&#8217;s activities and its interactions with government representatives. The Hubei Writers Association has also been involved in organizing cultural events, including a conference that brought together women writers from around the world, thereby promoting literary discussions on a global scale.

In response to the challenges posed by the outbreak, the association has facilitated the return of writers to their creative endeavors, signaling a revival of cultural activities. Additionally, its members have participated in community assistance efforts, demonstrating a commitment to social engagement and support during difficult times. Overall, the Hubei Writers Association stands as a vital collective that not only nurtures literary talent but also plays an active role in the cultural and social fabric of Hubei.</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418,fd7d025a46189bb316ef893020b7e22d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MILITARY WORLD GAMES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Military World Games is an international multi-sport event that took place in Wuhan, leaving behind decorative lights that now contrast with the city's desolation."</data>
      <data key="d2">c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE WRITER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Writer is a colleague of the narrator who discusses the notion of 'winning a resounding victory against the virus,' prompting criticism from the narrator."</data>
      <data key="d2">c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUANAN SEAFOOD MARKET&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Huanan Seafood Market is a location in Wuhan, China, that gained notoriety as the epicenter of the early cases of the novel coronavirus. It is situated near Central Hospital and has been linked to the initial outbreak of the virus. Due to health concerns associated with the coronavirus outbreak, the market was closed and is currently undergoing disinfection efforts. The closure and disinfection are part of the response to its identification as a significant site in the spread of the virus.</data>
      <data key="d2">4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf,70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Wuhan Central Hospital is a medical facility that gained significant attention during the outbreak of a viral illness, particularly due to the challenges faced by its medical professionals. It is known as the workplace of Dr. Li Wenliang, who was one of the doctors highlighting the severity of the situation. The hospital became a focal point for patients exhibiting flu-like symptoms, which raised concerns about the spread of the illness. Many medical staff at Wuhan Central Hospital encountered severe health issues while treating these patients, underscoring the intense pressures and risks associated with their work during this critical time.</data>
      <data key="d2">b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169,caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 1, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 1, 2020 marks a significant date during the coronavirus outbreak, reflecting on the situation and statistics related to the infection."</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ELDEST BROTHER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Eldest Brother is a university professor who shares information about the coronavirus outbreak with the family chat group."</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OTHER BROTHER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Other Brother works in Shenyang and expresses concern about the outbreak, suggesting the family huddle down to wait it out."</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SARS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">SARS, or Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome, is referenced as a previous outbreak that occurred in 2003. It has been compared to the current coronavirus situation, emphasizing concerns about contagion and the potential for widespread transmission. The comparisons highlight both the lessons learned from the SARS epidemic and the lessons that may have been forgotten in the context of the ongoing health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FAMILY CHAT GROUP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Family Chat Group is a communication platform where family members share information and updates about the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JIANGXIA DISTRICT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Jiangxia District is a location in Wuhan where the narrator resides, further away from the outbreak's epicenter."</data>
      <data key="d2">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN EVENING NEWS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan Evening News is a news outlet that reported on the closure of the Huanan Seafood Market, highlighting the early response to the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. WANG GUANGFA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Wang Guangfa is a specialist who was part of the team sent to investigate the outbreak in Wuhan and made significant statements regarding the virus's controllability."</data>
      <data key="d2">4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHONG NANSHAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Zhong Nanshan is a prominent Chinese doctor and respiratory expert known for his significant contributions during the coronavirus outbreak. He played a crucial role in raising public awareness about the possibility of human-to-human transmission of the virus, which influenced both public perception and response to the crisis. As a member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering, he arrived in Wuhan to uncover the truth about the outbreak and actively questioned the accuracy of reports regarding the situation. His insights and updates on the duration of quarantine measures were vital for the community, and many in Wuhan awaited his approval to lift these restrictions. Through his efforts, Zhong Nanshan has been instrumental in enhancing the understanding of the virus and its transmission, solidifying his status as a key figure in addressing the public health emergency.</data>
      <data key="d2">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,4ff73e560b2adc17ec7edf9507bb1ecf,88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae,fd7d025a46189bb316ef893020b7e22d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. WANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Mr. Wang is a multifaceted individual who plays several important roles within his community. He is a medical professional dedicated to curing the sick and assisting the injured during a health crisis, showcasing his commitment to public health and welfare. In addition to his medical responsibilities, Mr. Wang also serves as a security guard at the Literary and Arts Federation, where he contributes to the distribution of food supplies to residents, further demonstrating his dedication to supporting those in need. Furthermore, Mr. Wang has a personal dimension to his life, as he has a mother who lives alone and is concerned about her well-being during the quarantine, highlighting his familial responsibilities and the emotional challenges he faces amidst the ongoing health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa,96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI PROVINCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Hubei Province is a region in China that has been at the center of the coronavirus outbreak, significantly impacting its large population, particularly in the city of Wuhan, which is located within the province. The region has faced a severe health crisis characterized by high infection and mortality rates, with confirmed cases exceeding 70,000. The outbreak has led to the implementation of strict measures, including quarantine orders, as well as fluctuations in new confirmed cases.

The health crisis has resulted in limited access to hospital care, contributing to high death rates. Additionally, Hubei Province has reported a significant number of police officers infected with the virus. Throughout this challenging period, the province has received aid from other regions and is now in the process of welcoming back its residents and medical teams. There have been calls for government officials in Hubei Province to accept responsibility for their actions during the outbreak, highlighting the need for accountability in managing the crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,a45ab7ca6e1942a4732b13ef47f6587f,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HEALTHCARE FACILITIES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Healthcare Facilities refer to medical institutions that are preparing for an influx of patients during the health crisis, particularly in neighboring provinces."</data>
      <data key="d2">96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PATIENT A&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Patient A is referenced in the context of transmitting an illness to Patient B, highlighting the dynamics of disease transmission."</data>
      <data key="d2">96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PATIENT B&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Patient B is mentioned as a recipient of the illness from Patient A, illustrating the spread of the infectious disease."</data>
      <data key="d2">96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHENGDU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Chengdu is a city in China that serves as a significant geographical reference point, particularly noted for its connection to Mr. Liu, who sent fish to the narrator from this location. The city is also recognized for its air pollution issues, which prompted the narrator to receive an N95 mask from a classmate. Additionally, Chengdu has experienced an earthquake that had repercussions for residents of Wuhan who were present during the outbreak. This combination of factors highlights Chengdu's environmental challenges and its impact on the broader region.</data>
      <data key="d2">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YOUNG VOLUNTEERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Young Volunteers are a group of tens of thousands of individuals in Wuhan who are actively working to combat the outbreak, using social media to organize their efforts."</data>
      <data key="d2">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHEN CUN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chen Cun is a writer who shared videos documenting daily life in Wuhan after the quarantine, highlighting the experiences of residents during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHONGQING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Chongqing is a major city in China that has been highlighted in the context of travel challenges during an epidemic. A family from Chongqing attempted to travel to Guizhou, showcasing the difficulties associated with movement during this time. Additionally, the city is noted as a location where a husband and wife encountered restrictions at a border, further illustrating the impact of the epidemic on mobility and travel within the region.</data>
      <data key="d2">9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GUIZHOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Guizhou is a province in China that has been referenced in the context of travel and regional restrictions. It is noted as the origin of a wife who is unable to cross into Chongqing, indicating potential barriers faced by individuals during this period. Additionally, Guizhou serves as the destination for a family traveling from Chongqing, which underscores the challenges of regional travel during the epidemic. This highlights the complexities and limitations imposed on movement between these two areas during a time of heightened health concerns.</data>
      <data key="d2">9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DOCTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Doctor" is a compassionate individual who traveled to Wuhan to aid patients during the coronavirus outbreak, demonstrating remarkable kindness and dedication. As a friend of the narrator, The Doctor works on the front lines of the epidemic in Wuhan, providing valuable insights into the critical situation and the challenges related to medical supplies. Through their efforts, The Doctor exemplifies a commitment to helping others during a time of crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE EPIDEMIC&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Epidemic" refers to the widespread outbreak of the coronavirus, which has significantly impacted many individuals and families, particularly in Wuhan and its surrounding areas. This situation has led to severe health and social challenges, resulting in considerable loss and emotional distress among the population. The broader implications of "The Epidemic" encompass not only the immediate health crisis but also the profound consequences it has had on the community and society as a whole.</data>
      <data key="d2">2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LOCAL HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Local Hospitals are smaller medical facilities in Wuhan facing challenges due to limited resources and attention during the epidemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE FAMILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Family consists of a married couple and their children, illustrating the personal impact of travel restrictions during the epidemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUCHANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Wuchang is a district in Wuhan, China, that has been prominently mentioned in the context of lifting quarantines during a health crisis. The area has been a focal point for reflections on both historical events and the current conditions surrounding quarantine measures. Additionally, Wuchang has been noted for having virus patients, highlighting its significance during the health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HANKOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Hankou is a district in Wuhan, China, notable for its historical significance and its role during various crises. It is mentioned as a location where virus patients are located, highlighting its relevance during health outbreaks. The author reflects on Hankou as the place where they grew up, emphasizing the personal impact of the outbreak on the community. Historically, Hankou is recognized for its collaborative spirit, as it was a place where residents worked together to assist those in the neighboring district of Wuchang during a siege. Additionally, Hankou has been referenced in the context of the quarantine situation, further underscoring its importance during times of crisis. Overall, Hankou serves as a significant district in Wuhan, marked by its historical context and its response to contemporary challenges.</data>
      <data key="d2">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HANYANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Hanyang is a district in Wuhan, China, recognized for its historical significance and its role in various crisis situations. It is noted for its cooperation with the neighboring district of Hankou, particularly in assisting Wuchang during times of need. Additionally, Hanyang has been mentioned in the context of quarantine measures, highlighting its relevance in public health and safety protocols.</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CITY OF WUCHANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The City of Wuchang refers to a historical setting in the author's novel, depicting a time of siege and starvation nearly a hundred years ago."</data>
      <data key="d2">9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MUNICIPAL GOVERNMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The municipal government is responsible for issuing proclamations to assure citizens about the availability of supermarkets during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DOCTOR FRIEND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The doctor friend is a medical professional who discusses the potential number of coronavirus infections and the nature of symptoms with the author."</data>
      <data key="d2">9d1b23dde4b17acb2dfd0472a9ab0471</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE PEOPLE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The People refers to ordinary citizens affected by the health crisis, who are experiencing fear and chaos during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 5, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 5, 2020 marks a significant date during the coronavirus outbreak, reflecting on the impact of the pandemic on ordinary people."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LEISHENSHAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Leishenshan Hospital is a significant medical facility located in Wuhan, China, that has played a crucial role in the response to the coronavirus outbreak. Established as an emergency hospital, it has been actively involved in treating patients during the health crisis, particularly those with critical conditions. The hospital has been noted for its substantial medical efforts and has been a focal point for managing the influx of patients during the pandemic. Director Wang has been a prominent figure at the hospital, making significant comments regarding the situation and the challenges faced. As a Level One facility, Leishenshan Hospital is integral to the healthcare response in Wuhan, contributing to the overall efforts to combat the outbreak and provide care to those in need.</data>
      <data key="d2">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed,4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE COMMUNIST PARTY SCHOOLS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chinese Communist Party Schools are designated as Level Three facilities for isolating suspected cases of infection during the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MILITARY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Military has been involved in Wuhan's response to the coronavirus outbreak, contributing to the efficiency of the efforts against the virus."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PATIENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Patients are individuals affected by the coronavirus outbreak, many of whom have deferred their own medical care to allow doctors to focus on fighting the virus. Additionally, patients are seeking medical treatment and are facing increased costs and challenges due to the pandemic and associated healthcare policies. This situation highlights the complex impact of the pandemic on patients, as they navigate both the immediate effects of the virus and the broader implications for their healthcare needs.</data>
      <data key="d2">548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DOCTORS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Doctors are healthcare professionals who are actively engaged in treating patients affected by the coronavirus outbreak, often at the expense of their own patients' needs."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A FAMOUS PAINTER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A Famous Painter is mentioned as being in critical condition due to the coronavirus, highlighting the personal impact of the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"YL is a friend of the narrator who knows cinematographers affected by the coronavirus, illustrating the widespread impact of the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GILEAD SCIENCES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Gilead Sciences is an American pharmaceutical company that has developed a new drug called remdesivir, which is being tested for effectiveness against the virus in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;REMDESIVIR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
      <data key="d1">Remdesivir is an antiviral medication developed by Gilead Sciences that has been identified as effective in combating the novel coronavirus, underscoring its importance during the ongoing health crisis. It has been referred to as "the people's hope" by Chinese specialists and is currently undergoing clinical trials at Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital. Clinical evidence suggests that Remdesivir is particularly effective in treating patients with coronavirus, especially in clinical settings.</data>
      <data key="d2">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748,d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3,e27a49f034d2f2f425ddd0e46dee9822</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN JINYINTAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital is a medical facility in Wuhan where clinical trials for remdesivir are being conducted."</data>
      <data key="d2">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE &amp; EXHIBITION CENTER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan International Conference &amp; Exhibition Center is one of the locations where temporary hospitals are being set up to accommodate patients during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN KETING EXPO AREA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Wuhan KeTing Expo Area is a designated location in Wuhan that was utilized for the establishment of temporary hospitals during the coronavirus outbreak. This area played a crucial role in managing the health crisis by providing additional medical facilities to accommodate the surge in patients.</data>
      <data key="d2">b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FENG TIANYU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Feng Tianyu is a cultural history professor from Wuhan University who is involved in the management of temporary hospitals during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YAN ZHI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Yan Zhi is an administrator at a temporary hospital in Wuhan, where they play a crucial role in overseeing the setup of the facility and ensuring that patient care and comfort are prioritized during a challenging time. Yan Zhi is dedicated to meeting the needs of patients, ensuring that their care is managed effectively in the temporary hospital environment.</data>
      <data key="d2">36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHONGNAN HOSPITAL OF WUHAN UNIVERSITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Zhongnan Hospital of Wuhan University is a prominent medical institution where Dr. Peng Zhiyong is employed. The hospital has been significant in the context of the coronavirus pandemic, as it was the site of critical observations regarding the virus. Additionally, a pulmonologist at Zhongnan Hospital treated patients affected by the coronavirus and shared valuable insights and experiences related to the disease. This institution has played a crucial role in understanding and managing the impacts of the virus.</data>
      <data key="d2">36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DR. LI WENLIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Dr. Li Wenliang was an ophthalmologist at Central Hospital in Wuhan, whose actions during the coronavirus outbreak have made him a significant figure in the public consciousness. He became known for his early warnings about the virus, alerting colleagues and the public to the emerging health crisis. Despite his efforts to raise awareness, he faced challenges as a whistleblower, which highlighted the struggles faced by medical professionals during this time.

Tragically, Dr. Li contracted the virus himself and ultimately passed away on February 6, 2020. His death not only underscored the dangers faced by healthcare workers but also transformed him into a symbol of truth and sacrifice in the fight against the pandemic. Following his passing, he was honored by citizens in Wuhan with a motorcade send-off, reflecting the deep respect and gratitude felt by the community for his courageous actions. Dr. Li Wenliang's legacy continues to resonate as a reminder of the importance of transparency and the sacrifices made by those in the medical field during crises.</data>
      <data key="d2">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,81ac5d9d3486351095e7556baea13868,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;QUARANTINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The term "Quarantine" refers to a public health measure that was implemented in Wuhan to control the spread of the coronavirus. This measure involved the enforced isolation of individuals, significantly affecting the daily lives of residents. During this period, residents of Wuhan and surrounding areas were restricted from leaving their homes due to the outbreak, marking a time of considerable change and adjustment in their routines. Additionally, the quarantine period also reflects the author's personal experience of being confined due to health concerns, highlighting the broader implications of such measures on individual lives and communities.</data>
      <data key="d2">36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,c45145c12a7fedd7064529e344fa3e04</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN TONGJI HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan Tongji Hospital is another medical facility in Wuhan where medical personnel also succumbed to the virus during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE QUARANTINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Quarantine" refers to a public health measure implemented in Wuhan to control the spread of the coronavirus, significantly impacting the daily lives of nearly nine million residents. This measure involved a period of isolation lasting 59 days, during which residents were confined to their homes to prevent further transmission of the virus. The Quarantine not only affected the daily routines of the people in Wuhan but also had implications for their mental health. It was characterized by strict lockdown measures aimed at isolating individuals in Wuhan and surrounding areas, thereby addressing the urgent need to contain the respiratory disease. Overall, "The Quarantine" represents a critical response to a public health crisis, with profound effects on the community's social and psychological well-being.</data>
      <data key="d2">11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,1a74ad918264f9c92231f7eea81aa970,2014d81b9f4aeb008dab606a9f719b7a,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LI PEIGEN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Li Peigen is the university president who expressed condolences for a professor who passed away due to the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LANTERN FESTIVAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Lantern Festival is a traditional Chinese festival that marks the end of the Lunar New Year, celebrated with colorful displays and festivities. It occurs on the fifteenth day of the Lunar New Year and is a significant cultural event. The festival has continued to be celebrated even during the pandemic, highlighting its importance in Chinese culture and community.</data>
      <data key="d2">368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CCTV&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">CCTV, or China Central Television, is a state-run media organization in China that serves as a prominent broadcaster. It produces a variety of shows, including culturally significant programs such as the Lantern Festival Special, which highlights important cultural celebrations. Additionally, CCTV plays a crucial role in news dissemination, particularly noted for its coverage during significant events such as outbreaks, thereby influencing news consumption patterns in the country.</data>
      <data key="d2">5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;I AM A SINGER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"I Am a Singer is a popular television show that is anticipated by viewers, providing entertainment during challenging times."</data>
      <data key="d2">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE TEMPORARY HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Temporary Hospitals refer to medical facilities that were established to treat patients during the coronavirus outbreak, playing a crucial role in the community's healthcare response. Specifically, these hospitals were set up to accommodate the surge of coronavirus patients during the peak of the epidemic in Wuhan. Their establishment was essential in managing the overwhelming number of cases and ensuring that patients received the necessary medical attention during this critical time.</data>
      <data key="d2">1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MEDICAL PROFESSIONALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Medical Professionals include doctors, nurses, and other healthcare workers who are actively involved in fighting the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SANITATION WORKERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Sanitation Workers are responsible for maintaining cleanliness in the city, continuing their work despite the challenges posed by the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE POLICEMEN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Policemen are law enforcement officers who are stationed at various locations, including hospitals, to maintain order during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Coronavirus is a novel viral outbreak that has evolved into a global pandemic, originating in Wuhan and subsequently affecting communities worldwide. This viral infection has led to significant health crises, resulting in increased illness and death, and has prompted widespread discussions about various treatment methods, including traditional Chinese medicine. The outbreak has caused profound changes in daily life and health management, leading to lockdowns and heightened demand for medical facilities. 

As a global health crisis, the Coronavirus has significantly impacted public health protocols and has altered the way individuals and communities interact. Quarantine measures have been implemented, affecting the lives of many, including the characters in various narratives that reflect the societal changes brought about by the pandemic. The ongoing outbreaks continue to challenge healthcare systems and have led to a reevaluation of community support and health management strategies. Overall, the Coronavirus represents a significant event that has reshaped the lives of individuals and families, highlighting the interconnectedness of health and society in the face of a global crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,05facbc17efc22acf453283e5f155f6b,0ea87bb3f7f4f08e19bd21127da9be59,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637,6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47,a45ab7ca6e1942a4732b13ef47f6587f,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3,d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3,e27a49f034d2f2f425ddd0e46dee9822,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A THOUSAND ARROWS PIERCING THE HEART&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A Thousand Arrows Piercing the Heart is a novella that features a protagonist named Li Baoli, who is referenced in the context of the emotional struggles during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MORTUARY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Mortuary is a place where deceased individuals are processed, and its employees are depicted as overwhelmed by the number of deaths due to the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEDICAL PROFESSIONALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Medical professionals are individuals who have volunteered to assist in Hubei, providing critical support and medical care during the crisis. They have been working tirelessly to save patients during the coronavirus outbreak, facing immense challenges in their efforts. These dedicated individuals play a crucial role in the healthcare system, especially during times of crisis, demonstrating their commitment to patient care and public health.</data>
      <data key="d2">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 10, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 10, 2020 marks a date during the health crisis when the situation in Wuhan is expected to improve, reflecting hope among the residents."</data>
      <data key="d2">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;VOLUNTEERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Volunteers are individuals from various provinces who have come to Hubei to provide medical assistance and supplies during the health crisis. They have stepped up to help during the coronavirus outbreak, often at risk of infection while delivering essential services. These dedicated individuals play a crucial role in supporting the healthcare system and assisting those affected by the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Central Hospital is a prominent healthcare institution located in Wuhan, which has played a critical role in the fight against the coronavirus epidemic. The hospital has been heavily impacted by the outbreak, becoming a frontline facility for treating infected patients. It has been identified as one of the most dangerous areas in terms of infections during the crisis, facing severe challenges that include the loss of several physicians and significant mortality among patients.

The leadership of Central Hospital has faced criticism for perceived negligence in managing the outbreak, raising questions about its response to the health crisis. Notably, the hospital is where Dr. Li Wenliang worked, along with other medical professionals such as Dr. Jiang Xueqing, Ai Fen, Dr. Yi Fan, and Dr. Hu Weifeng, who have all been involved in the treatment of patients during this tumultuous period.

Central Hospital has experienced a multitude of deaths during the coronavirus outbreak, which has further highlighted the challenges it faces, including the critical illness of several doctors due to severe complications from the virus. The institution has become a focal point for significant events related to the outbreak, underscoring its vital role in the healthcare system amidst the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">05facbc17efc22acf453283e5f155f6b,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,81ac5d9d3486351095e7556baea13868,8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde,a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LI WENLIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Li Wenliang was an ophthalmologist at Central Hospital in Wuhan who became widely recognized for his early warnings about the coronavirus outbreak. His proactive stance in alerting the public to the dangers of the virus made him a symbol of the fight against COVID-19, as he raised alarms that were initially overlooked by authorities. Despite his efforts, he faced censure for speaking out, which highlighted significant issues of communication and professional responsibility within the medical community. Li Wenliang's legacy is deeply tied to the struggles faced by medical professionals during the epidemic, and he is remembered by many as a whistleblower who exemplified the importance of transparency in healthcare. His Weibo page became a platform for public mourning following his untimely passing during the crisis, marking a significant moment in the narrative of the outbreak and the broader discourse surrounding it.</data>
      <data key="d2">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d,2014d81b9f4aeb008dab606a9f719b7a,2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,8475b5acce1676914c613935d50901d6,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062,f7d4aedaaebf83b5bb28320eecdc7d6c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROFESSOR LIN ZHENGBIN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Professor Lin Zhengbin was an organ transplant specialist at Tongji Hospital who passed away during the viral outbreak, leaving a significant impact on the community."</data>
      <data key="d2">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SUNNY SKY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Sunny Sky is a well-known restaurant in Wuhan that provided meals for patients at temporary hospitals during the viral outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TEMPORARY HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Temporary Hospital refers to the medical facilities set up in Wuhan to treat patients during the viral outbreak, providing essential care and support."</data>
      <data key="d2">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BAIBUTING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Baibuting is a significant location in Wuhan, known for hosting a large-scale banquet that raised concerns during the outbreak. This event highlighted the area's relevance in the context of public health. Additionally, Baibuting holds personal significance for the author, who worked as a porter there, indicating its importance in their life and experiences.</data>
      <data key="d2">1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;VICTOR HUGO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Victor Hugo is a renowned author whose quote about silence resonates with the author, reflecting on the importance of speaking out."</data>
      <data key="d2">1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JOAQUIN PHOENIX&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Joaquin Phoenix is an actor whose Oscar acceptance speech inspired the author to consider the importance of using one's voice for the voiceless."</data>
      <data key="d2">1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHEN XIAOQING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chen Xiaoqing is a writer and host of a documentary series on CCTV, known for his connection to the city of Wuhan and its culture."</data>
      <data key="d2">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TANG XIAOHE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Tang Xiaohe is a neighbor of the narrator and a close friend of Mr. Xiang Xinran, highlighting her personal connections within the community. During the lockdown, she shares videos of her granddaughter, which serve as a source of joy and connection for the narrator. Additionally, Tang Xiaohe is a painter who appreciates the narrator's writing about Wuhan, indicating a mutual admiration for the city's culture. She also shares photos of blooming flowers, offering a vibrant contrast to the author's reflections on the pandemic, further enriching the sense of community and shared experiences during challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d2">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b,a1228c3edf57aa00b38f80de4ec91c5e,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MRS. CHENG LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mrs. Cheng Li is the wife of Tang Xiaohe, who, along with her husband, has lived in Wuhan for a long time and understands the narrator's sentiments about the city."</data>
      <data key="d2">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE BIRTH OF A BABY BOY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Birth of a Baby Boy is a positive event shared by the narrator's colleague, symbolizing hope amidst the difficulties faced by the people of Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DOG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Dog is the narrator's pet, who has been a part of their life for 16 years, representing companionship during tough times."</data>
      <data key="d2">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHANG MANLING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhang Manling is a writer from Yunnan who sent aid to the people of Hubei during the outbreak and has a historical connection to Yingjiang."</data>
      <data key="d2">8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YINGJIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Yingjiang is a prefecture in Yunnan Province, known for its community support during the crisis, sending aid to Hubei."</data>
      <data key="d2">8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SACRIFICED YOUTH&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Sacrificed Youth is a novel by Zhang Manling that reflects on her experiences during the Cultural Revolution and has been adapted into a film."</data>
      <data key="d2">8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Li is mentioned as a person who has passed away, marking a significant emotional moment in the narrative."</data>
      <data key="d2">5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE FLAGS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chinese Flags represent a symbol of national pride that is being used by aid workers during their support efforts in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TEMPORARY HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Temporary Hospitals are established facilities designed to provide medical care during outbreaks, particularly during the surge of coronavirus cases. These facilities were notably constructed in Wuhan to accommodate the increasing number of patients during the peak of the outbreak. They offered not only medical treatment but also essential services such as food and social activities for those recovering. Throughout their operation, Temporary Hospitals received visits from political leaders, highlighting their significance in the public health response. However, it is important to note that these Temporary Hospitals have since been closed following the decline in cases.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PUBLIC SERVANTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Public Servants are individuals sent by the government to assist those in need during the outbreak, often seen carrying Chinese flags."</data>
      <data key="d2">5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE COMMUNIST PARTY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Communist Party is referenced in the context of a song sung by officials and medical professionals to patients, highlighting political sentiments during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YANGTZE DAILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Yangtze Daily" is a mainstream media outlet that serves as a newspaper, providing comprehensive reports on the coronavirus outbreak and its impact on the region. Throughout the pandemic, "Yangtze Daily" has faced criticism for its reporting, yet it is recognized for maintaining high editorial standards. Additionally, the newspaper has published essays that reflect the sentiments of the public during the COVID-19 outbreak, thereby offering a platform for public expression and engagement with the community's concerns.</data>
      <data key="d2">9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,e27a49f034d2f2f425ddd0e46dee9822,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI GOVERNMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Hubei Government is the local authority tasked with managing the response to the COVID-19 outbreak in Wuhan and the broader Hubei province. It has faced criticism for its handling of the crisis, particularly regarding the effectiveness of its measures. In addition to overseeing the overall response to the pandemic, the Hubei Government has organized a goodbye ceremony for service workers who have contributed to the fight against the virus. Furthermore, in response to a spike in COVID-19 cases, the government took decisive action by firing prison officials, highlighting its commitment to addressing the challenges posed by the outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d2">603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. LIU SHOUXIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Liu Shouxiang was a famous master of traditional Chinese painting whose death during the COVID-19 outbreak was mourned by the community."</data>
      <data key="d2">e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;COVID-19 OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The COVID-19 Outbreak refers to the global pandemic that originated in Wuhan in late 2019, significantly impacting not only the local region but also the broader world. This outbreak has led to a series of health and social challenges, prompting various responses from healthcare systems and governments worldwide. As the pandemic unfolded, it necessitated widespread health and safety measures to mitigate its effects on public health and safety.</data>
      <data key="d2">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062,fd7d025a46189bb316ef893020b7e22d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. LIU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Mr. Liu is a multifaceted character residing in Chengdu, known for his kindness and friendship, particularly through his involvement in sending fresh fish to the narrator. He is also recognized as a painter, a connection established through a neighbor, which highlights a personal bond during the challenging times of the outbreak. Additionally, Mr. Liu serves as a representative from the Wuhan Botanical Garden, where he proposed a quarantine model aimed at addressing the difficulties presented by the coronavirus outbreak. This combination of artistic talent, personal connection, and proactive engagement in public health showcases Mr. Liu's diverse contributions to his community.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PITTSBURGH&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Pittsburgh is a US city that has donated medical supplies to Wuhan, highlighting international support during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YANGTZE ARTS MAGAZINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Yangtze Arts Magazine is a publication where one of the narrator's friends works, contributing to community support efforts."</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE COMMUNIST PARTY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Chinese Communist Party (CCP) is the ruling political party in China, playing a significant role in the country's governance and public health response during the pandemic. The CCP has been involved in sending skilled professionals to assist local communities affected by the outbreak, demonstrating its commitment to public welfare. Additionally, the party has requested public expressions of gratitude from citizens, reflecting its desire to foster a sense of unity during challenging times. However, there are also calls for the CCP to express gratitude towards the citizens and take responsibility for the outbreak, indicating a complex relationship between the party and the public. Furthermore, representatives of the CCP are engaged in various cultural and governance activities, such as involvement in the Hubei Writers Association, highlighting the party's influence in both political and cultural spheres.</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,24f82cd50519ba6e59f128ccf5c821f6,5a58a4c5bcc46fb9d4065918796e6b69,973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;AID PROVISIONS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Aid Provisions are the supplies and support being sent to Hubei to assist those affected by the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FANG FANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Fang Fang is a professional writer and former chair of the Hubei Writers Association, renowned for her outspoken criticism of government officials during the coronavirus outbreak in Wuhan. She is best known for her diary, which documents her personal experiences, thoughts, and feelings while under quarantine, as well as her reflections on the lives of the people in Wuhan. Through her writings, Fang Fang has expressed a strong social mission and literary skill, capturing the local events and the emotional landscape of the epidemic.

Despite her literary contributions, Fang Fang has faced criticism and scrutiny for her perspectives, particularly regarding the content of her diary. Additionally, she has been mistakenly associated with a controversial book about edible animals, which led to online attacks against her. Throughout these challenges, she has continued to document her experiences and express her frustrations over public criticism of her work.</data>
      <data key="d2">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YANGZHOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Yangzhou is a city in China known for its spring scenery, mentioned in the context of longing for a trip there."</data>
      <data key="d2">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1</data>
    </node>
