    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 15, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 15, 2020, marks a specific date during the coronavirus outbreak, reflecting the urgency and emotional weight of the situation described in the text."</data>
      <data key="d2">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </node>
