      <data key="d2">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUMANISTIC SPIRIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Humanistic Spirit refers to the principles of compassion and empathy that should guide actions, especially in times of crisis, as discussed in the context of the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHILDHOOD FRIEND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Childhood Friend is a personal connection of the narrator, whom they wish a speedy recovery, indicating a sense of care and concern during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MIDDLE SCHOOL CLASSMATE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Middle School Classmate is another personal connection of the narrator, whose husband is seeking kidney dialysis treatment, highlighting the struggles faced by individuals during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIANG LIGANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Xiang Ligang is a controversial media figure on Weibo, recognized for his significant following and his ability to influence public opinion. He has garnered criticism for his posts related to various outbreaks, which reflect the ongoing tensions in public discourse. His stance often downplays the seriousness of these situations, positioning him as a critic whose views contrast sharply with the experiences and concerns expressed by others. This combination of rumor-spreading and dismissive commentary has made him a polarizing figure in discussions surrounding public health and safety.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XU HAODONG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xu Haodong is a self-described photographer from Wuhan who expresses hostility towards the narrator, reflecting the divisive atmosphere on social media."</data>
      <data key="d2">c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LIU FAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Liu Fan was a dedicated nurse who tragically contracted the coronavirus while working on the front lines of healthcare. Despite her efforts to care for patients, she ultimately succumbed to the illness, underscoring the significant dangers faced by healthcare workers during the pandemic. Her death serves as a poignant reminder of the personal impact of the outbreak on individuals and their families.</data>
      <data key="d2">c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHINESE NEW YEAR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Chinese New Year is a significant cultural celebration that coincides with the onset of the health crisis, affecting social gatherings and traditions."</data>
      <data key="d2">c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DUAN ZHENGCHENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Duan Zhengcheng was a professor at Huazhong University of Science and Technology who tragically died from the novel coronavirus, marking a significant loss for the university."</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN UNION HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Wuhan Union Hospital is a medical facility located in Wuhan, China, that plays a significant role in the treatment and care of patients during the outbreak of the novel coronavirus. In addition to its efforts in managing cases related to the virus, Wuhan Union Hospital also accepts non-novel coronavirus patients, thereby contributing to the broader healthcare response during the crisis. This dual focus highlights the hospital's commitment to providing comprehensive medical care amidst challenging circumstances.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI PEOPLE&#8217;S HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hubei People&#8217;s Hospital is the third hospital in Wuhan that is accepting non-novel coronavirus patients, essential for managing healthcare needs during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ROGUE VIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Rogue Virus refers to the novel coronavirus, characterized by its unpredictable behavior and the challenges it poses to public health."</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROVINCIAL LITERARY AND ARTS FEDERATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Provincial Literary and Arts Federation is an organization that plays a significant role in community response and management, particularly during crises. It serves as a work unit through which orders and communications are disseminated, indicating its importance in facilitating a structured community response. Additionally, the Federation is mentioned in the context of managing housing complexes during lockdowns, highlighting its involvement in ensuring the welfare and organization of community living during challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHANG KAI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Chang Kai was a film director associated with the Hubei Film Studio and was the younger brother of Liu Fan, who also tragically succumbed to the coronavirus. As a victim of the outbreak, Chang Kai's final words hold considerable significance, serving as a testament to his experiences and the broader narrative of seeking justice for those affected by the pandemic. His last words are suggested to be memorialized for future generations, highlighting his impact on the community and the importance of his story in the context of the outbreak. Through his work and the circumstances surrounding his death, Chang Kai left a lasting impression on those around him.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PANSUO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Pansuo is a Weibo user who commented on the online discourse surrounding the outbreak, criticizing the way information is shared."</data>
      <data key="d2">5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PEOPLE&#8217;S DAILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"People&#8217;s Daily is a major state-run newspaper in China, mentioned as a source of news during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DIRECTOR WANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Director Wang is a medical professional from Leishenshan Hospital who expresses confidence in the improvement of the outbreak situation."</data>
      <data key="d2">4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEDICAL WORKERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Medical workers are professionals who have come from all over China to Wuhan to provide crucial support during the outbreak. They have played a significant role in addressing the overwhelming numbers of patients and have faced substantial challenges in their efforts. Their contributions have been vital in improving the situation in Wuhan during this critical time.</data>
      <data key="d2">4c986d95fbf69302998d67747722f245,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;NOVEL CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Novel Coronavirus is a newly identified virus that emerged in late 2019, leading to a global outbreak and significant health and economic impacts. This outbreak has resulted in a major health crisis characterized by widespread illness and death, severely affecting healthcare systems and altering societal norms. The virus is responsible for the COVID-19 pandemic, which has prompted extensive discussions about treatment methods, including those proposed by Li Yuehua. Overall, the Novel Coronavirus has raised substantial health concerns worldwide, highlighting the urgent need for effective responses to manage its effects.</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,68d1018c902661392b4e20435e4961ad,8119bda66f27343b4be177610dcff2af,f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HEALTHCARE PROVIDERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Healthcare Providers are professionals working in hospitals and clinics, who faced shortages during the outbreak, impacting their ability to care for patients."</data>
      <data key="d2">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CREMATORIUMS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Crematoriums are facilities responsible for the disposal of deceased bodies, which faced shortages and challenges during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TELECOMMUNICATIONS COMPANY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Telecommunications Company is involved in efforts to contact family members of deceased individuals by using their cellphone numbers."</data>
      <data key="d2">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GOVERNMENT ORDER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Government Order refers to the strict quarantine measures issued to control the spread of the virus, requiring residents to stay indoors."</data>
      <data key="d2">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;E-COMMERCE SITES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"E-commerce Sites are online platforms that adapted their sales methods to meet the needs of consumers during the quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DOG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Dog is a 17-year-old pet belonging to the narrator, providing companionship during the quarantine and illustrating the narrator's home life. As the dog ages, it is experiencing health issues that necessitate veterinary care, highlighting the challenges of caring for an elderly pet while also emphasizing the bond shared between the narrator and the dog during this time.</data>
      <data key="d2">c45145c12a7fedd7064529e344fa3e04,f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PEOPLE&#8217;S LIBERATION ARMY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The People&#8217;s Liberation Army is the armed forces of China, mentioned in the context of their involvement in the city during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;KENGEE BREAD SET MEAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Kengee Bread Set Meal is a food item ordered by the narrator, representing the challenges of food supply during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TURNING POINT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Turning Point refers to a critical moment in the outbreak when the number of infected patients is expected to peak, as discussed by medical professionals."</data>
      <data key="d2">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TRADITIONAL CHINESE MEDICINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) is a holistic approach to health that has been practiced for over 5,000 years, emphasizing the importance of balance and the use of natural remedies. This ancient medical practice has gained significant recognition for its effectiveness, particularly during the coronavirus outbreak, where a notable percentage of patients received TCM as a form of treatment. TCM's long-standing history and its application in modern health crises highlight its enduring relevance and the value it offers in promoting wellness and recovery.</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DOCTOR FRIEND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "Doctor Friend" is a character who serves as a medical professional providing valuable insights and updates regarding the coronavirus outbreak. This character discusses various aspects of the crisis, including hospital conditions, accountability, and the effectiveness of treatment methods. Additionally, the Doctor Friend offers clarifications about the situation surrounding the outbreak and the implications of the closure of temporary hospitals. Through these discussions, the Doctor Friend plays a crucial role in informing the narrator and others about the ongoing challenges and developments related to the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAO GENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Lao Geng is an individual who plays a significant role in managing a grocery delivery group, demonstrating a strong commitment to community involvement, especially during challenging times. Additionally, Lao Geng is an old classmate of the narrator, who assists by forwarding valuable information regarding grocery delivery options. Through these efforts, Lao Geng contributes to supporting the community and facilitating access to essential services.</data>
      <data key="d2">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 18, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 18, 2020, marks a date during the outbreak when the author reflects on the situation in Wuhan and the impact of quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LITERARY AND ARTS FEDERATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Literary and Arts Federation is a significant entity located in Wuchang, Wuhan, serving both as a building where an author resides and as an organization deeply embedded in the local literary community. This federation has played an active role in community support efforts, particularly during the outbreak, by engaging in initiatives such as food distribution to assist those in need. Additionally, it has initiated a popular grocery delivery group that has garnered support and participation from local neighborhoods, further solidifying its commitment to community welfare and connection to the arts.</data>
      <data key="d2">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE AUTHOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Author is a retired professional writer with a notable reputation in Wuhan, having published nearly 100 books throughout their career. In addition to their extensive body of work, The Author is currently an independent writer who is documenting personal experiences and reflections during the outbreak in Wuhan. This dual role highlights both their established literary contributions and their ongoing engagement with contemporary events.</data>
      <data key="d2">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,ecdbc80cd38edf6145de3f6de4c35bb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PAN XIANGLI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Pan Xiangli is a friend who offers emotional support and promises a meal together, representing social connections during isolation."</data>
      <data key="d2">e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUNAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hunan is a neighboring province to Hubei, with residents contributing support during the outbreak and being part of social discussions."</data>
      <data key="d2">e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUAGANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Huagang is a region that received medical support from Hunan, noted for its high recovery rate during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FULAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fulan is a term used to refer to residents of Hunan, particularly in a humorous context among friends."</data>
      <data key="d2">e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CULTURAL REVOLUTION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Cultural Revolution is a historical period in China that some ultra-leftists wish to return to, causing societal tensions."</data>
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A SOFT BURIAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A Soft Burial is a novel written by the narrator, which faced criticism from a group of people online."</data>
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"TA is a reader who left a message on the narrator's WeChat post, expressing concern for the narrator's well-being."</data>
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE PAINTER FROM NEW YORK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Painter from New York is a friend of the narrator who donated 100,000 yuan to aid during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE PAINTER FROM GERMANY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Painter from Germany is another artist who committed to donating 100,000 yuan and has a personal connection to the narrator."</data>
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE ULTRA-LEFTISTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1" />
      <data key="d2">dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SHANDONG PROVINCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Shandong Province is a region in China known for its humanitarian efforts during the coronavirus outbreak. The Blue Sky Aid Team, originating from Shandong Province, returned after providing essential humanitarian aid to Wuhan. Additionally, Shandong Province contributed to the relief efforts by donating food supplies, including celery, to support the affected population in Wuhan during this challenging time.</data>
      <data key="d2">48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DR. LIU ZHIMING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Dr. Liu Zhiming was the Director of Wuchang Hospital, recognized for his honesty and exceptional talent within the medical community. His passing during the coronavirus outbreak deeply affected the public, leading to widespread mourning and emotional tributes from many who respected and admired his contributions to healthcare.</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SU FAMILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Su Family is a group of Chinese painters who have committed to donating funds for medical supplies to support Wuhan during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE VOLUNTEERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Volunteers are individuals who have come together to assist in various community efforts during the coronavirus outbreak in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SHIPMENT OF MEDICAL SUPPLIES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Shipment of Medical Supplies refers to the delivery of essential medical supplies to Wuhan, which was supported by donations from various individuals and organizations."</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DONATION OF CELERY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Donation of Celery refers to the act of donating two tons of celery from Shandong Province to the residents of Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Coronavirus Outbreak refers to a global pandemic that began in late 2019, originating in Wuhan, China. This outbreak has significantly impacted healthcare systems, communities, and daily life across the globe. It has led to widespread quarantines, public health measures, and community mobilization efforts aimed at supporting those affected. The pandemic has caused severe health crises, including widespread infection and loss of life, particularly in Wuhan and the surrounding Hubei Province. The emotional distress and societal disruption resulting from the outbreak have been profound, prompting various responses from individuals and communities. As the situation escalated in early 2020, it became clear that the outbreak would have lasting implications for health, society, and the economy, affecting not only Wuhan but also countries worldwide.</data>
      <data key="d2">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,1a74ad918264f9c92231f7eea81aa970,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,39d6ae4d79ba80953eb86122bce3240d,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26,f7d4aedaaebf83b5bb28320eecdc7d6c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUCHANG HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuchang Hospital is a medical facility where Dr. Liu Zhiming served as Director, playing a significant role in the healthcare of the community."</data>
      <data key="d2">9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN UNIVERSITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Wuhan University is a prestigious educational institution located in China, renowned for its beautiful campus and academic excellence. It holds significant cultural value, particularly noted for its cherry blossoms, which evoke fond memories for individuals like Fang Fang from her college days. The university has been a pivotal place for many students, including the narrator, who pursued higher education there and resided in Dorm Eight with classmates, marking it as an important part of their academic lives.

In recent times, Wuhan University has faced challenges due to the outbreak of a virus, which tragically resulted in the loss of a PhD student, underscoring the profound impact of the pandemic on the academic community. Despite these difficulties, the university remains active in cultural and literary spheres, as evidenced by the invitation extended to Yan Geling to deliver a lecture. Additionally, the university's international alumni have been taking bold actions in response to the ongoing crisis, reflecting the institution's global influence and the resilience of its community.</data>
      <data key="d2">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,39b4b0551e8b6bf986b203e943245b3f,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f,9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CCP ASSESSMENT GROUP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The CCP Assessment Group is a newly established group in Wuhan responsible for overseeing the response to the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHONGSHAN PARK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Zhongshan Park is a public space located in Wuhan that has recently become deserted due to the ongoing outbreak, illustrating the significant impact of the pandemic on daily life and public areas. The current situation has transformed what was once a vibrant location into a deserted area, emphasizing the broader effects of the crisis on community spaces.</data>
      <data key="d2">9b3b89c18ca285cf79a2fb9f3355fa5f,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LIBERATION PARK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Liberation Park is another location noted for its emptiness, reflecting the broader context of social distancing and quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAYAN ISLAND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Layan Island is referenced as a biking destination, indicating a place of leisure that is currently affected by the situation."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. XIANG XINRAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Xiang Xinran is an architect, nearly 80 years old, who expresses gratitude through an essay during the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CORONAVIRUS REPORT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "Coronavirus Report" is a local community publication dedicated to providing updates and information about the coronavirus situation in the area. It serves as a vital resource for residents, offering insights and developments related to the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIANG XINRAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiang Xinran is a resident of Wuhan who expresses deep concern for the impact of the coronavirus outbreak on his community and reflects on his experiences during this crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SOUTHCENTRAL ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN INSTITUTE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Southcentral Architecture and Design Institute is the workplace of Xiang Xinran, where he was assigned after graduating in 1963."</data>
      <data key="d2">d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHANCELLOR LIU DAOYU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Chancellor Liu Daoyu is a government official who is particularly focused on the well-being of the elderly during a quarantine period. He is a resident of Wuhan and usually has a helper to assist him. During the outbreak, he was checked on by Xiang Xinran, highlighting the community's concern for vulnerable individuals like him.</data>
      <data key="d2">940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAO DAO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Lao Dao is an old classmate of the narrator, whose elderly parents are quarantined and in good health."</data>
      <data key="d2">940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI DAILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hubei Daily is a local newspaper where a famous editorial writer was infected with the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEBRUARY 21, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"February 21, 2020 marks a significant date during the coronavirus outbreak, reflecting on the impact of quarantine and community health."</data>
      <data key="d2">940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DR. PENG YINHUA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dr. Peng Yinhua was a young doctor who tragically passed away at the age of 29 after being infected while working on the front lines against the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIAO XIANYOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiao Xianyou was a patient in Wuhan who left behind a poignant final testament before his death, expressing love for his wife and a desire to donate his body to the nation."</data>
      <data key="d2">db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WRITERS ASSOCIATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Writers Association is a supportive group of writers who have come together during the pandemic to assist one another by sharing supplies and personal experiences. In addition to fostering a sense of community among its members, the association also functions as a professional organization dedicated to supporting writers more broadly. It provides care and resources specifically for retired members, ensuring that all writers, regardless of their career stage, receive the support they need.</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,ecdbc80cd38edf6145de3f6de4c35bb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;RIVER ISLE QUARANTINE MODEL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The River Isle Quarantine Model is a proposed strategy by Mr. Liu to utilize islet areas and decommissioned ships for housing patients during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TIANXINGZHOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Tianxingzhou is a geographical area of roughly 22 square kilometers, larger than Macau, and is proposed as a site for housing patients during a health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MACAU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Macau is a geographical area with a population of 600,000, mentioned as a point of comparison to Tianxingzhou."</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINA NEWS AGENCY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">China News Agency is a government media organization in China that is recognized for its relatively relaxed standards compared to other media outlets, although it remains prudent on certain sensitive topics. The agency employs Xia Chunping and plays a significant role in reporting during health crises, contributing to the dissemination of information during such critical times.</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HEADLINES TODAY (JINRI TOUTIAO)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Headlines Today, also known as Jinri Toutiao, is a prominent news organization recognized for its significant role in the rapid dissemination of information online. The platform has showcased various content, including the narrator's diary, which highlights the swift spread of information in the digital age. Additionally, Headlines Today has featured the author on its site, further demonstrating its extensive reach and influence in the media landscape.</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE HEALTH CRISIS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Health Crisis refers to the ongoing situation in Wuhan, characterized by an outbreak that has necessitated a lockdown and a substantial need for medical assistance and supplies. This crisis has resulted in widespread quarantines, leading to significant social and economic impacts on the affected region and beyond.</data>
      <data key="d2">3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SINA WEIBO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Sina Weibo is a social media platform in China recognized for its liberal policies for expression, where the author actively publishes content."</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WESTERN MEDICINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">Western Medicine is a system of medicine that emphasizes the use of pharmaceuticals and surgery. It has been in widespread use in China for only a few decades, marking a significant shift in the country's medical practices. Often contrasted with traditional Chinese medicine, Western medicine represents modern medical practices that have gained prominence in China during this relatively short period.</data>
      <data key="d2">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;INSTITUTE OF CHINESE MEDICINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Institute of Chinese Medicine is an educational institution dedicated to the study and practice of traditional Chinese medicine. It provides individuals with the opportunity to learn about various aspects of this ancient medical system and offers programs that enable students to obtain medical licenses in the field. Through its curriculum, the Institute emphasizes the importance of traditional practices and knowledge, equipping students with the skills necessary to pursue careers in Chinese medicine.</data>
      <data key="d2">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637,68d1018c902661392b4e20435e4961ad</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHU FENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chu Feng is a colleague of the narrator who experienced positive health effects after using traditional Chinese herbal medicine."</data>
      <data key="d2">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MY DOCTOR FRIEND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"My Doctor Friend" is a medical professional who offers valuable insights into the challenges encountered by healthcare workers and patients during the coronavirus pandemic. Additionally, this individual advocates for the effectiveness of traditional Chinese medicine in treating various ailments, particularly in the context of the ongoing health crisis. Through their work, "My Doctor Friend" aims to bridge the gap between modern medical practices and traditional healing methods, providing a holistic perspective on health and wellness during these unprecedented times.</data>
      <data key="d2">548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MY COLLEGE CLASSMATE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"My College Classmate is an educator at the Institute of Chinese Medicine who promotes traditional Chinese medicine and critiques Western medicine."</data>
      <data key="d2">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN CURSES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Wuhan Curses refer to expressions of frustration from residents of Wuhan regarding the handling of the coronavirus outbreak, which have gained attention from government offices."</data>
      <data key="d2">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GROUP-BUYING MODEL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Group-Buying Model is a method of purchasing goods collectively, which has shown shortcomings during the coronavirus outbreak in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIA SISI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xia Sisi was a young doctor who tragically died from the coronavirus at the age of 29, leaving behind a two-year-old child."</data>
      <data key="d2">32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUANG WENJUN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Huang Wenjun was a male doctor who died from the coronavirus at the age of 40, highlighting the risks faced by healthcare professionals during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAO YANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Lao Yang is a former Group Leader from college who has assumed a senior government post in Beijing, maintaining connections with former classmates."</data>
      <data key="d2">32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAO XIA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Lao Xia is a former classmate who has worked in media since graduation and is actively involved in reporting on the coronavirus outbreak and providing community services."</data>
      <data key="d2">32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DORM EIGHT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dorm Eight" is the building at Wuhan University where the author and their classmates resided during their time in school. This dormitory symbolizes a shared experience and history among the students, representing a significant aspect of their university life.</data>
      <data key="d2">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHANG OUYA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhang Ouya is a journalist who publicly called for the replacement of leaders supervising the fight against the coronavirus, demonstrating bravery in the face of adversity."</data>
      <data key="d2">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIAO ZHOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiao Zhou is responsible for managing the area where the author lives, indicating a role in community support during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN OUTBREAK PREVENTION CONTROL CENTER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Wuhan Outbreak Prevention Control Center is responsible for issuing commands related to the management of the outbreak in Wuhan, indicating its role in public health and safety."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DAO BO&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dao Bo is a colleague who shares a friendly relationship with the narrator, often exchanging food and helping each other."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. LU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Lu is the store manager who shows kindness by sending over a box of craftsman bread to the narrator."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;COMMUNITY WORKERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Community Workers are individuals mobilized to conduct surveys and collect information in households to control outbreaks. They play a crucial role in providing essential services during such crises, often facing significant challenges and risks while assisting the public. Their efforts are vital in managing health emergencies and ensuring that communities receive the support they need.</data>
      <data key="d2">63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BEIJING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">Beijing is the capital city of China and serves as a significant location in the context of the narrator's old classmates and communication regarding an outbreak. During a crisis, Beijing has been involved in implementing policies that affect the entry of residents from Hubei, particularly those from Wuhan. The city has imposed restrictions on individuals coming from Hubei to manage the situation effectively.</data>
      <data key="d2">5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5,941fd97efac4d3db43e927529ff925c4,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINA TELECOM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"China Telecom is one of the three largest telecommunications companies in China, proposed to be involved in establishing a National Emergency Response Network."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINA MOBILE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"China Mobile is one of the three largest telecommunications companies in China, suggested to assist in contacting cellphone users for health check-ins."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINA UNICOM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"China Unicom is one of the three largest telecommunications companies in China, recommended to help in the National Emergency Response Network."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WECHAT PAY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"WeChat Pay is one of the largest private e-pay companies in China, proposed to be part of the National Emergency Response Network for health tracking."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ALIPAY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Alipay is one of the largest private e-pay companies in China, suggested to assist in tracking health check-ins during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DJI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"DJI is a company known for its drones, proposed to be utilized for patrolling virus zones and delivering announcements during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHANG AD&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhang AD is a graduate from the same department as the author, who provided recommendations for managing the viral outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHANG GUANGNIAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhang Guangnian is the father of Zhang AD and the lyricist of the famous song Yellow River Cantata."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIAN XINGHAI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xian Xinghai is the composer of the Yellow River Cantata and related to the author through a family connection."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CAIXIN MEDIA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Caixin Media is a news organization that reported on the challenges faced by retirement homes during the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;NATIONAL EMERGENCY RESPONSE NETWORK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The National Emergency Response Network is a proposed system to manage health check-ins and track the spread of the virus in China."</data>
      <data key="d2">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YELLOW RIVER CANTATA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
