    <node id="&quot;HAN DONG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Han Dong is a poet from Nanjing who has been stuck in Hubei for over 40 days during the lockdown. His experience underscores the personal impact of the pandemic on individuals, illustrating the challenges faced during this unprecedented time.</data>
      <data key="d2">24f82cd50519ba6e59f128ccf5c821f6,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb</data>
    </node>
