    <node id="&quot;DR. JIANG XUEQING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Dr. Jiang Xueqing was a respected physician and the Director of the Department of Thyroid and Breast Cancer at Central Hospital. His passing on March 1 during the outbreak has profoundly impacted his colleagues, leading to a heartfelt tribute in the form of a group photo. His contributions to the medical field and the care he provided to patients are remembered fondly by those who worked alongside him.</data>
      <data key="d2">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa</data>
    </node>
