      <data key="d2">73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;NATIONAL HEALTH COMMISSION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The National Health Commission is a governmental body in China that is responsible for public health. It plays a crucial role in managing and implementing public health measures, particularly in response to the coronavirus outbreak. The Commission's responsibilities include overseeing the country's health policies and coordinating efforts to address viral outbreaks, ensuring the safety and well-being of the population.</data>
      <data key="d2">73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE FOURTH ROUND OF THE SHIRKING RESPONSIBILITY SUMMIT MEETING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Fourth Round of the Shirking Responsibility Summit Meeting is an event focused on addressing the government's response to the coronavirus outbreak in Wuhan. This meeting serves as a platform for discussing the responsibilities and actions taken in relation to the management of the viral outbreak, highlighting the measures implemented to tackle the crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JANUARY 14 MEETING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The January 14 Meeting refers to a significant teleconference held to discuss measures to combat the viral outbreak before public acknowledgment of its spread."</data>
      <data key="d2">88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FORTY-TWO THOUSAND WARRIORS&quot;">
