    <node id="&quot;AI FEN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Ai Fen is a physician at Central Hospital who has gained significant attention online for her role in sounding alarms about the coronavirus outbreak. She emphasized the importance of professional integrity and responsibility during this public health crisis, highlighting the challenges posed by the censorship of information related to the pandemic. Her actions have underscored the critical need for transparency and accountability in the medical community during times of crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PEOPLE MAGAZINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"People Magazine is a publication that featured an article about Ai Fen, which has been subject to censorship, raising questions about the information being suppressed."</data>
      <data key="d2">3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">China is a country that is often discussed in relation to its government officials and their responsibilities, particularly concerning issues of resignations and accountability. Additionally, China faces challenges from the presence of ultra-leftists, which are perceived as a threat to its future and the necessary reforms within the nation.</data>
      <data key="d2">8127e2d84213dc7f69446ae542408f8b,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WUHAN CITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
