      <data key="d2">b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SOUTHERN WEEKLY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Southern Weekly is a magazine that published an investigative report regarding the situation in Wuhan Central Hospital, shedding light on critical issues."</data>
      <data key="d2">b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DR. YANG FAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Dr. Yang Fan is a frontline doctor at Wuhan Central Hospital, where he is actively involved in treating patients. He emphasizes the severity of the situation faced by his colleagues, many of whom are critically ill. His role highlights the challenges and pressures experienced by medical professionals during this critical time.</data>
      <data key="d2">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WANG PING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Wang Ping is the Assistant Director at Wuhan Central Hospital. Currently, he is critically ill and experiencing multiple organ failure due to the circumstances surrounding patient care.</data>
      <data key="d2">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LIU LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Liu Li is a Medical Ethics Committee Member at Wuhan Central Hospital, where they have been critically ill with severe complications while navigating the ongoing health crisis. Tragically, Liu Li succumbed to the novel coronavirus, underscoring the profound impact of the pandemic on healthcare workers. Their experience reflects the challenges faced by medical professionals during this unprecedented time.</data>
      <data key="d2">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df,b71c5e2269adc5d8c094d58432376169</data>
    </node>
