    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YI FAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Dr. Yi Fan is the Assistant Director of the Thoracic Surgery Department at Central Hospital. Recently, he has faced critical health issues but has since recovered from a critical condition.</data>
