      <data key="d1">Dr. Hu Weifeng, also known as Hu Zha, is the Assistant Director of the Department of Urology at Central Hospital. He has recently recovered from a critical condition, indicating a significant improvement in his health status after facing serious medical challenges.</data>
      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044</data>
