      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI DAILY NEWS AND MEDIA GROUP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Hubei Daily News and Media Group is a prominent media organization based in Hubei Province, specifically recognized as the largest media group in Wuhan. It oversees a diverse array of media platforms, including multiple newspapers, magazines, websites, and other outlets, establishing itself as a significant source of news and information in the region.</data>
      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YANGTZE DAILY NEWSPAPER GROUP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Yangtze Daily Newspaper Group is a prominent media organization based in Hubei Province, recognized as the second largest media group in Wuhan. It shares a similar structure and influence with the Hubei Daily News and Media Group, indicating its significant role in the regional media landscape. The group is dedicated to providing comprehensive news coverage in the area, contributing to the dissemination of information and public discourse in Hubei.</data>
      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE APPALACHIAN TRAIL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Appalachian Trail is a hiking trail that Old Fox completed, representing a significant personal achievement."</data>
      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WHISTLEBLOWER INCIDENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Whistleblower Incident refers to the events surrounding Dr. Li Wenliang and Dr. Ai Fen, highlighting issues of accountability and information dissemination during a health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE NEW YEAR CONCERT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Chinese New Year Concert is a significant cultural event that took place in January 2020, coinciding with the early days of the coronavirus outbreak. During this event, Bao Jie performed as the lead singer, showcasing his vocal talent prior to his infection. The concert garnered attention from various media organizations, highlighting its importance in the context of the unfolding global health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Mr. Li is a character who reflects on his relationships with his two friends, Bao Jie and Su Huajian, through an essay that explores their lives and the significant impact of the coronavirus on them. Additionally, Mr. Li is a member of the Xi-Wen Choir, where he has expressed concern over Su Huajian's sudden absence. He reminisces about their shared experiences in the choir, indicating a deep bond and the emotional weight of their friendship during challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BAO JIE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Bao Jie is a friend of Mr. Li and a talented singer who was a member of the senior choir. Tragically, Bao Jie was affected by the coronavirus, which impacted his health. Additionally, Bao Jie is recognized as a member of the Xi-Wen Choir, where he is mentioned alongside Su Huajian, another choir member who also faced health risks during the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SU HUAJIAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Su Huajian is remembered as a friend of Mr. Li and is noted in Mr. Li's essay as a victim of the coronavirus. He was an active member of the Xi-Wen Choir, where he participated enthusiastically before his sudden passing on March 6. His contributions to the choir and his friendship with Mr. Li highlight the impact of his loss on those who knew him.</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WHAMPOA MILITARY ACADEMY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Whampoa Military Academy is an institution associated with an arts group that Bao Jie joined, which prepared for a Chinese New Year concert."</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XI-WEN CHOIR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The Xi-Wen Choir is a local choir based in Wuhan, established in 1938. Over the years, it has evolved to include members beyond its original alumni, expanding its reach within the community. The choir actively holds concerts, showcasing its musical talents and engaging with the public.</data>
      <data key="d2">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CONCERT LUNCHEON&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Concert Luncheon was an event held by the Xi-Wen Choir on January 9, marking the last time Mr. Li saw Su Huajian."</data>
      <data key="d2">db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JIANGXIA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Jiangxia is a geographical location where the author's neighbor lives, contributing to the author's reflections on nature during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d2">a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;YAN GELING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Yan Geling is a writer living in Berlin who has been closely following the events in Wuhan and has written an essay about the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MARIO VARGAS LLOSA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mario Vargas Llosa is a renowned writer whose books have reportedly been ordered to be removed from bookstores, causing shock and concern in the literary community."</data>
      <data key="d2">2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CENSORSHIP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Censorship refers to the suppression of information and ideas, which is highlighted as a significant issue in the context of the coronavirus outbreak in China."</data>
      <data key="d2">2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LAO TONG CITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Lao Tong City is a famous restaurant in Wuhan, renowned for its tofu skin, and is a significant part of the local culinary culture."</data>
      <data key="d2">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZENG GUANGCHENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zeng Guangcheng is the founder of Lao Tong City, a notable figure in Wuhan's culinary history."</data>
      <data key="d2">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. ZENG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Mr. Zeng is a multifaceted character who has published a trilogy and is deeply concerned about his elderly mother living alone during a quarantine. In addition to his literary pursuits, he is the eldest grandson of Zeng Guangcheng and is actively engaged in documenting the history of his family and their restaurant. This dual focus on both personal and familial responsibilities highlights Mr. Zeng's commitment to his loved ones and his heritage.</data>
      <data key="d2">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE STORY OF LAO TONG CITY AND THE ZENG FAMILY OF HANKOU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Story of Lao Tong City and the Zeng Family of Hankou is a literary project undertaken by Mr. Zeng to document his family's history and the restaurant's legacy."</data>
      <data key="d2">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;HUBEI UNIVERSITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hubei University is the institution where Mr. Zeng's mother resides in the faculty dorm during the quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SHANCHUN COUNTY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Shanchun County is a location in Huanggang where residents are experiencing the lifting of quarantine restrictions."</data>
      <data key="d2">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEDICAL AID TEAMS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Medical Aid Teams are groups of medical workers who came to help during the outbreak in Wuhan, providing critical support to the community."</data>
      <data key="d2">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CREATIVE WRITING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Creative Writing is an activity that Mr. Zeng's mother engages in daily, showcasing her resilience during the quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THANK YOU GESTURE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Thank You Gesture refers to the collective expression of gratitude from Wuhan residents towards the medical aid teams as they departed."</data>
      <data key="d2">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;XIANGYANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Xiangyang is a city that has honored its medical aid teams by recording their names and offering them lifetime free admission to scenic destinations."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SICHUAN PROVINCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Sichuan Province is a region in China from which a medical team traveled to Hubei to assist during the health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHAO YINGMING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhao Yingming is a medical worker who has returned home after serving in Hubei, and her husband humorously promised to do household chores for a year."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHINESE INTERNATIONAL STUDENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Chinese International Students are individuals who studied abroad and are now returning to China after the outbreak has been controlled."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;WAR OF RESISTANCE AGAINST JAPAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The War of Resistance against Japan refers to a historical conflict where many sought refuge, drawing parallels to current events of seeking safety during crises."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;QUARANTINE LIFTING TIMELINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Quarantine Lifting Timeline outlines the schedule for lifting restrictions in Hubei and Wuhan, indicating a return to normalcy."</data>
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SEEKING REFUGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1" />
      <data key="d2">3d2800441ca7b567a9560d875635ba68</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ER XIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Er Xiang is a character who manages an official account known as "Er Xiang&#8217;s Eleven Dimensions of Space." She plays a crucial role in assisting the narrator during a challenging period, particularly when the narrator's Weibo account was frozen. As a writer with a verified official public account on WeChat, Er Xiang helps the narrator share diary entries, demonstrating her support and significant contribution during this difficult time. The author acknowledges her efforts and the importance of her assistance in navigating the challenges posed by the account blockage.</data>
      <data key="d2">7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,8127e2d84213dc7f69446ae542408f8b,8475b5acce1676914c613935d50901d6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SARS EPIDEMIC&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The SARS Epidemic is recognized as a significant health crisis that occurred in the early 2000s, characterized by a severe outbreak of a viral infection. This epidemic had a profound impact on public health and led to changes in hospital practices and safety measures. Its relevance is particularly noted in the context of the current situation in Wuhan, where lessons learned from the SARS outbreak continue to inform health protocols and responses to infectious diseases.</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SHENZHEN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Shenzhen is a city in China known for its warm climate, which played a role during the SARS epidemic by allowing for better ventilation in hospitals."</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROVINCIAL PEOPLE&#8217;S CONGRESS MEETING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Provincial People&#8217;s Congress Meeting is an annual gathering of government officials in China to discuss and make decisions on various political matters."</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROVINCIAL POLITICAL CONSULTATIVE CONFERENCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Provincial Political Consultative Conference is an annual event in China where political advisors and officials convene to discuss policies and governance."</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BAI HUA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Bai Hua is a talented poet and playwright known for his works during the Cultural Revolution, including a poem that resonates with the themes of youth and experience."</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CULTURAL REVOLUTION&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">The Cultural Revolution was a socio-political movement in China that lasted from 1966 to 1976. It was marked by widespread upheaval and a campaign against perceived bourgeois elements within society. This movement aimed to reinforce communist ideology and eliminate capitalist and traditional elements from Chinese culture, leading to significant social, political, and economic changes during that period.</data>
      <data key="d2">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;REFORM ERA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "Reform Era" refers to a significant period in China that began in the late 1970s, characterized by extensive economic and political reforms that transformed the country's structure and policies. However, this era is currently perceived to be at risk due to the influence of ultra-leftists, which are viewed as a hindrance to the progress made during this transformative time.</data>
      <data key="d2">8127e2d84213dc7f69446ae542408f8b,8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MY CHILD&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"My Child is a 16-year-old individual receiving advice and reflections from the narrator about education, independent thought, and personal growth."</data>
      <data key="d2">8addb1ba85a3edd5b064d6a87d33e55f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;NATIONAL LETTER WRITING DAY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"National Letter Writing Day is humorously referred to by Yi Zhongxue as a day when many people wrote open letters, reflecting a moment of community engagement during quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A WUHAN DIARY BRIMMING WITH MALICIOUS INTENTIONS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This is an essay forwarded to the narrator that critiques their diary, indicating ongoing tensions and controversies surrounding their writings."</data>
      <data key="d2">8475b5acce1676914c613935d50901d6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;QI JIANHUA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">Qi Jianhua is an author known for his contentious writings during the pandemic. His essay, titled "A Wuhan Diary Brimming with Malicious Intentions," has been criticized for spreading false information. This controversy surrounding his work is further highlighted by the fact that an essay he published on Investigative Web was taken down, reflecting the sensitive nature of his writing during this period.</data>
      <data key="d2">2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;INVESTIGATIVE WEB&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Investigative Web is a platform that publishes a variety of essays and articles, including those that are controversial and have ignited public debate. Among the content featured on the website is an essay by Qi Jianhua, which has faced accusations of slandering the narrator. This highlights the platform's role in disseminating provocative material that can lead to significant discussions and disputes within the public sphere.</data>
      <data key="d2">2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEDICAL ETHICS COMMITTEE MEMBER LIU LI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Liu Li is identified as a Medical Ethics Committee Member who died from the novel coronavirus, marking a significant loss in the medical community."</data>
      <data key="d2">2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MARCH 20, 2020&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"March 20, 2020 is the date on which the narrator reflects on the current state of the coronavirus situation in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d2">2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PEKING UNIVERSITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">Peking University is a prestigious educational institution located in China, recognized for its high academic qualifications and standards. It serves as a significant center for scholarly critique and education, where Professor Zhang teaches. Additionally, Peking University is affiliated with Professor Zhang Yiwu, who contributes to the academic discourse on various topics, including the pandemic and related issues. The institution is noted for its influential role in shaping academic discussions and fostering intellectual growth within the community.</data>
      <data key="d2">11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHANG YIWU&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhang Yiwu is a prominent professor at Peking University who has publicly addressed the controversies surrounding the pandemic and the writings about it."</data>
      <data key="d2">a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A LETTER FROM A GROUP OF HIGH SCHOOL STUDENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This letter is a response from high school students addressing issues raised during the pandemic, showcasing their independent thinking and observations."</data>
      <data key="d2">a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PROFESSOR ZHANG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Professor Zhang is a literary figure who critiques the author's diary and is known for his strong opinions and controversial judgments in academia."</data>
      <data key="d2">11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHOU XIAOPING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhou Xiaoping is mentioned as a model youth praised by Professor Zhang, indicating his significance in the context of the author's critique."</data>
      <data key="d2">11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DR. ZHANG WENHONG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dr. Zhang Wenhong is a doctor in Shanghai known for his expertise and advice on managing the coronavirus outbreak, emphasizing personal protection measures."</data>
      <data key="d2">82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OVERSEAS CHINESE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Overseas Chinese refers to individuals of Chinese descent living abroad who contributed medical supplies to Wuhan during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OFFICE OF POVERTY ALLEVIATION AND DEVELOPMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Office of Poverty Alleviation and Development is a government body in China responsible for implementing policies to assist low-income families affected by the coronavirus."</data>
      <data key="d2">24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TAI CHI&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Tai Chi is a form of exercise that the letter writer's sister practiced daily before being confined at home due to the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CANCER PATIENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Cancer Patients are individuals who have been affected by the coronavirus outbreak, leading to interruptions in their treatment and care."</data>
      <data key="d2">24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION IN WUHAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Public Transportation in Wuhan refers to the resumption of normal transport services in the city as it begins to recover from the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d2">24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE LUNAR NEW YEAR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Lunar New Year is a significant holiday in China, during which the letter writer's sister-in-law's mother died due to lack of medical care."</data>
      <data key="d2">24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Medical Practitioners are healthcare professionals dealing with the complexities of treating patients during the pandemic, facing their own fears and challenges."</data>
      <data key="d2">548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ZHONGNAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Zhongnan Hospital is a medical facility in Wuhan that has been affected by the coronavirus, with its outpatient clinic closed but its emergency room operational."</data>
      <data key="d2">ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SHADOW DREAM TEAM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "Shadow Dream Team" is a dedicated volunteer group based in Wuhan, actively assisting individuals who are stranded in the city. Since the onset of the lockdown, the team has been focused on providing essential support, which includes planning for the safe return of those affected. Additionally, the group has been instrumental in delivering donated food and medical supplies to those in need, showcasing their commitment to helping the community during challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d2">941fd97efac4d3db43e927529ff925c4,ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MASSACHUSETTS GENERAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Massachusetts General Hospital is a medical institution affiliated with Harvard University, leading a project to share effective methods for treating coronavirus patients globally."</data>
      <data key="d2">ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;500 CHINESE-AMERICAN PHYSICIANS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"500 Chinese-American Physicians is a group of doctors aiming to address key issues related to the coronavirus and share insights on treatment methods."</data>
      <data key="d2">ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;Z&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Z is a person suffering from a mouth ulcer and a serious chronic health condition, requiring medical attention during a quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d2">54353bad2befd9d61191dd25ba0263f5</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;L'S OLD PARTNER&quot;">
