      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Xiao Yuan supports the narrator by delivering masks in Wuhan, highlighting community solidarity during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE LITERARY AND ARTS FEDERATION&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Literary and Arts Federation is a location in Wuhan where significant interactions occur during the lockdown."</data>
      <data key="d5">a230706d366d287b5a4591eaaf7c6186</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;MAYOR ZHOU XIANWANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Mayor Zhou Xianwang is responsible for leading the municipal government of Wuhan during the outbreak, directly impacting the city's response."</data>
      <data key="d5">23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">7.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is recognized as the epicenter of the outbreak, experiencing the most severe effects of the viral epidemic. The city has faced significant distress among its residents, who have encountered numerous challenges due to the health crisis. The outbreak has had a profound impact on Wuhan's population and healthcare system, leading to drastic changes in daily life. In response to the crisis, the city has implemented significant lockdown measures, prompting various community responses. Overall, Wuhan has been directly affected by the outbreak, highlighting the extensive challenges faced by its residents during this difficult time.</data>
      <data key="d5">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,23d7b47883d11f234a69aa99b5f286b4,5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5,8124652946d2a60444c90e0a3706521b,8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;EAST RIVER GARDEN LANE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">East River Garden Lane is a biking route located in Wuhan. Currently, it is described as deserted due to the pandemic and the quarantine measures that have been implemented in the area.</data>
      <data key="d5">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUOSHENSHAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">5.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Huoshenshan Hospital is located in Wuhan and was specifically constructed to address the healthcare crisis arising from the coronavirus outbreak. This facility plays a crucial role in treating patients during this health emergency, providing essential medical support to the community. The establishment of Huoshenshan Hospital reflects Wuhan's efforts to manage the medical challenges posed by the outbreak, ensuring that adequate care is available for those affected.</data>
      <data key="d5">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PROFESSOR LIU CHUAN&#8217;E&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Professor Liu Chuan&#8217;e is a resident of Wuhan who is affected by the emotional and social impacts of the coronavirus crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;JIANG ZIDAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Jiang Zidan provides traditional medicine advice to residents in Wuhan, helping them cope with health issues during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">e8105e46cc3831c70abcbabad8edbcaf</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is recognized as the epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak, which originated in the city and has had a profound impact on its residents and the community as a whole. The outbreak has revealed new characteristics and challenges faced by the people of Wuhan, who have experienced significant hardships due to severe lockdown measures implemented to control the spread of the virus. As the city most affected by the pandemic, Wuhan has been central to discussions regarding the implications of the outbreak, with its healthcare system facing immense pressure. The initial cases and responses to the virus were concentrated in Wuhan, making it a focal point in the global narrative surrounding the coronavirus outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,2423a98cbf380f6e2dfa8c89eed4b6ed,2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;AUTHOR&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The author expresses a strong commitment to the people of Wuhan during the coronavirus outbreak, indicating a personal connection."</data>
      <data key="d5">9588379e66312b7114543c3aed2a9b4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">17.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is the city where the Coronavirus outbreak was first identified, making it the epicenter of the epidemic and a focal point for the global response to the pandemic. The outbreak has led to a public health crisis in Wuhan, resulting in significant lockdowns and changes in daily life for its residents. As the origin of the virus, Wuhan has faced severe health challenges and public scrutiny, experiencing profound impacts on its population, including emotional distress and significant social challenges. The city has been central to discussions surrounding the pandemic, with the majority of cases and responses concentrated there. Wuhan's experience highlights the challenges of controlling the virus and managing its effects on the community, as it navigates the consequences of the outbreak and the measures taken to mitigate its spread.</data>
      <data key="d5">16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,24930dd33f36a0ab439b76b9f78b2dd2,26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda,2d702d808dc0983b5a009535ca71a6c6,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a,5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a,82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408,ac0300cb099cefe43a5c7d0656313435,ae5f337979abdf9e93ce2001ba7eeca2,dfb6674717edcd1b507ed271953bbf39</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HONGSHAN DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Hongshan Department of Transportation plays a crucial role in managing transportation logistics in Wuhan during the quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d5">679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;OFFICER XIAO&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Officer Xiao represents the local authorities in Wuhan who are actively helping residents during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">679f442d0cee20509148a0adeb4ebc0a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE VIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is the city that is experiencing the effects of The Virus outbreak, which has led to quarantine measures and significant community distress. As the epicenter of this health crisis, Wuhan faces considerable challenges in managing the outbreak and its repercussions on public health and safety.</data>
      <data key="d5">c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE MILITARY WORLD GAMES&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Military World Games were held in Wuhan, leaving behind decorations that now serve as a reminder of normalcy amidst the ongoing crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUBEI WRITERS ASSOCIATION&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Hubei Writers Association, based in Wuhan, plays a significant role in supporting local writers and addressing the challenges posed by the pandemic. Its members are directly impacted by the events occurring in the city, which has led the association to actively contribute to community support efforts. The Hubei Writers Association has sent members to assist in Wuhan, demonstrating their commitment to the local community during these challenging times.</data>
      <data key="d5">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,c74fab649e0e555219cd986800fcd418</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUANAN SEAFOOD MARKET&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan is the city where the Huanan Seafood Market is located, which is the epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan Central Hospital is situated in Wuhan and is a key location for patients during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;JIANGXIA DISTRICT&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Jiangxia District is a part of Wuhan, indicating the geographical context of the narrator's residence during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">caadf962e601168cde3ab59608d7641b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;MR. WANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Mr. Wang is actively engaged in healthcare efforts in Wuhan, focusing on curing the sick and assisting the injured during the ongoing crisis. His commitment to helping others is further underscored by the personal impact of the situation, as his mother resides in Wuhan, which is currently under quarantine. This quarantine has significantly affected her daily life and care, adding a personal dimension to Mr. Wang's professional responsibilities in the region.</data>
      <data key="d5">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa,96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUBEI PROVINCE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is a major city located within Hubei Province, which has been significantly affected by the coronavirus outbreak. The high infection rates in Hubei Province are closely linked to the situation in Wuhan, as the city is central to the health crisis being discussed. The impact of the outbreak is felt throughout the entire region, with specific case numbers reported for both Wuhan and Hubei Province. Additionally, the province has reported a notably high number of infections among police officers during the outbreak, further highlighting the widespread effects of the crisis. Overall, Wuhan's status as a key urban center within Hubei Province underscores the regional implications of the health emergency.</data>
      <data key="d5">32a647b4ed6b9cec72592c3d59b51208,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,48f71f719bc3d7a90495615cc8668f0e,96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff,a45ab7ca6e1942a4732b13ef47f6587f,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HEALTHCARE FACILITIES&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Healthcare Facilities in neighboring provinces are preparing for patients from Wuhan, indicating a response to the health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">96d1b9c58350b57745013c6971a006ff</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CHENGDU&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan and Chengdu are two cities in China that share a geographical connection, particularly highlighted by the delivery of fish from Mr. Liu to the narrator. The narrator draws comparisons between the air quality and personal experiences in both cities during an outbreak, indicating a shared context of challenges faced by their residents. Additionally, there is a humorous connection between the two cities stemming from the impact of an earthquake in Chengdu, which affected Wuhan residents, fostering a sense of camaraderie during a difficult period. Overall, the relationship between Wuhan and Chengdu is characterized by both logistical ties and shared experiences in the face of adversity.</data>
      <data key="d5">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;YOUNG VOLUNTEERS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Young Volunteers are actively working in Wuhan to support the community during the outbreak, showcasing their commitment and resilience."</data>
      <data key="d5">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CHEN CUN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Chen Cun shared videos that document the experiences of Wuhan residents during the outbreak, connecting his work to the city's current situation."</data>
      <data key="d5">0bc629e093e4342af5865fab7f58e2ed</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE EPIDEMIC&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan is the epicenter of the Epidemic, experiencing severe impacts on its residents and healthcare system."</data>
      <data key="d5">f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE DOCTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is a city that became a focal point during the coronavirus outbreak, and The Doctor played a crucial role in addressing the health crisis there. The Doctor provides firsthand accounts of the situation in Wuhan, indicating a direct connection to the city's challenges during the pandemic. By traveling to Wuhan to offer aid, The Doctor underscored the city's significance in the global response to the outbreak, highlighting both the urgency of the health crisis and the efforts made to combat it.</data>
      <data key="d5">70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,f84389c17fb429f92b8c15bb5248e947</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE GOVERNMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d3">5.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Government is responsible for implementing and managing various measures in Wuhan during the health crisis caused by the coronavirus outbreak. This includes enforcing a lockdown and establishing price controls to stabilize the situation. The Government's actions and policies have significantly influenced the lives of Wuhan's residents, particularly through leadership changes and public health measures aimed at managing the crisis effectively. Their focus remains on addressing the health crisis and ensuring adequate hospital care, demonstrating a direct impact on the overall situation in Wuhan during this challenging period.</data>
      <data key="d5">16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3,527cd6baeddd98d25cc154a883dbb0ba,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,d1cc6f7c6f4e2faebe09261db22861ef,db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;GILEAD SCIENCES&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Gilead Sciences is developing remdesivir specifically for use in Wuhan to combat the outbreak, indicating a direct connection between the city and the organization."</data>
      <data key="d5">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN JINYINTAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital is located in Wuhan and plays a crucial role in the city's response to the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;FENG TIANYU&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Feng Tianyu, as a professor in Wuhan, is directly involved in addressing the challenges posed by the Outbreak in the city."</data>
      <data key="d5">b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;YAN ZHI&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Yan Zhi is a key figure in the administration of healthcare in Wuhan during the coronavirus outbreak, playing a significant role in directly impacting patient care in the city. His efforts in managing temporary hospitals have been crucial to the healthcare response in Wuhan, ensuring that the medical needs of the population are met during this challenging time.</data>
      <data key="d5">36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,b7955b3f9e06c3774b23917a41090748</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;DR. LI WENLIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">4.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Dr. Li Wenliang is a notable figure in Wuhan, recognized for his efforts to speak out about the coronavirus outbreak that has profoundly affected the city. He played a crucial role in alerting the community about the virus, making him a significant figure in Wuhan's response to the crisis. His actions and subsequent death resonated deeply with the city's residents, becoming a focal point for their emotional response during the outbreak. Dr. Li Wenliang is remembered by the people of Wuhan not only for his warnings but also for the impact he had on raising awareness about the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d5">368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b,36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;QUARANTINE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The quarantine measures were specifically enacted in Wuhan to control the spread of the coronavirus outbreak, significantly impacting millions of residents. These measures were a critical response to the public health crisis caused by the coronavirus, aimed at managing and mitigating the effects of the pandemic in the region.</data>
      <data key="d5">36beb6ff7483a2c562d33b9aa0fd5fbf,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE QUARANTINE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is the city that has been placed under quarantine as a direct response to the Coronavirus outbreak, which has significantly impacted the daily lives of its residents. The quarantine measures were implemented to control the spread of the virus, affecting the entire community and altering how residents navigate their lives during this health crisis. This significant event has created a direct link between Wuhan and the quarantine, highlighting the challenges faced by the population as they adapt to the restrictions and changes brought about by the outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d5">11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,1a74ad918264f9c92231f7eea81aa970,3924f78270d94ac683153f474f084511,3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c,63fc0690d8e8e6407e5bd58f20230a80,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,940cebaf3ab07fd2834e519f8dc05b5f,ee1c3739121c565e86473a0f5b9b5944</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;LI PEIGEN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Li Peigen, as the university president, is connected to the community in Wuhan, particularly in relation to the impact of the coronavirus on local education and health."</data>
      <data key="d5">368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;LANTERN FESTIVAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Lantern Festival is celebrated in Wuhan, marking a significant cultural event during the ongoing pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">368a2536cbf53473fcfdb5bb6a94e95b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE TEMPORARY HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan has established Temporary Hospitals to manage the influx of patients during the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE POLICEMEN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Policemen are stationed in Wuhan to ensure safety and order during the health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE SANITATION WORKERS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Sanitation Workers maintain cleanliness in Wuhan, contributing to public health efforts during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">e74e88082258029f6da479b11ff1f412</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">10.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is the city where the coronavirus outbreak originated, making it central to the event's impact and response. As the epicenter of the outbreak, Wuhan has experienced profound effects on public health and safety, leading to significant health crises and social challenges within the community. The outbreak has prompted extensive discussions about treatment methods and public health responses, as well as adaptations in daily life among residents.

In response to the escalating situation, Wuhan implemented strict quarantine measures and constructed temporary hospitals to manage the health crisis. Many residents have faced illness and loss due to the virus, highlighting the severe impact on the community. The ongoing challenges in controlling the virus's spread have further complicated the situation, necessitating continued community responses and adaptations. Overall, the coronavirus outbreak has significantly affected Wuhan, shaping the city's health landscape and social dynamics.</data>
      <data key="d5">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,0ea87bb3f7f4f08e19bd21127da9be59,5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb,a13ce419c16c812171a8f0609ebcfb47,a45ab7ca6e1942a4732b13ef47f6587f,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3,d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3,e27a49f034d2f2f425ddd0e46dee9822,e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;A THOUSAND ARROWS PIERCING THE HEART&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The novella A Thousand Arrows Piercing the Heart features themes and characters that resonate with the experiences of people in Wuhan during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE MORTUARY&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Mortuary in Wuhan is dealing with the high number of deaths resulting from the coronavirus outbreak, affecting the local community."</data>
      <data key="d5">d655504306cc8b53c02acaf9d17576e3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;ZHONG NANSHAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Zhong Nanshan, a prominent figure in the medical community, made a significant public statement in Wuhan regarding the virus, highlighting his influence in the city during the outbreak. His approval is crucial for the residents of Wuhan, as it signifies the potential lifting of quarantine restrictions that were imposed due to the pandemic. Furthermore, Zhong Nanshan's inquiries and actions are directly related to the situation in Wuhan during the coronavirus outbreak, underscoring his pivotal role in managing the health crisis in the region.</data>
      <data key="d5">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc,0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,94f757b20bd5e5a1834b6d4ae6d20dae</data>
    </edge>
