      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"February 10, 2020 is a significant date for the residents of Wuhan, as they anticipate improvements in their situation around this time."</data>
      <data key="d5">06e079c3e9edc095ce2abf1424d0adbc</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE VIRAL OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Viral Outbreak significantly impacted Wuhan, leading to the establishment of temporary hospitals and community efforts."</data>
      <data key="d5">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;BAIBUTING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Baibuting is a notable location within Wuhan, China, recognized for its role during a large gathering that raised public health concerns amid an outbreak. Additionally, Baibuting holds personal significance for the author, indicating a deeper connection to the city of Wuhan.</data>
      <data key="d5">1de8f51cd0e0d108a83dabdcd866f67d,3f8704dd72f25d452df3dea8b46c7b79</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CHEN XIAOQING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Chen Xiaoqing's work on a documentary series highlights the culture and history of Wuhan, connecting him to the city."</data>
      <data key="d5">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;TANG XIAOHE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Tang Xiaohe's admiration for the narrator's writing about Wuhan indicates a shared connection to the city and its culture."</data>
      <data key="d5">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE LOCKDOWN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Lockdown is a significant event affecting the city of Wuhan, implemented to control the spread of the coronavirus. This measure has led to widespread challenges for the residents of Wuhan, impacting their daily lives and routines. As the city where the Lockdown is enforced, Wuhan has faced numerous difficulties as a result of this public health intervention.</data>
      <data key="d5">548d34b58236a7b620d21d3773109475,55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE DOG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Dog symbolizes companionship and comfort for the narrator, who has deep ties to Wuhan and its community."</data>
      <data key="d5">55ae4eab571535c48f485b6f0e4dc82b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">5.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Central Hospital is a key medical facility located in Wuhan, China, and has played a crucial role in the city's response to the coronavirus outbreak. It has been a critical site for treating patients during this health crisis, serving as a focal point for medical attention. The hospital's significance is underscored by the challenges it has faced, including fatalities among its medical staff due to the virus. As a vital institution in Wuhan, Central Hospital has been instrumental in addressing the urgent healthcare needs of the community during the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4,8bcf953381c5940825f0aa7181e07bde</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PUBLIC SERVANTS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Public Servants are sent to Wuhan to provide aid during the outbreak, indicating their role in the crisis response."</data>
      <data key="d5">5de6fb969d67797c0c7839a2a6fcf7c5</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;YANGTZE DAILY&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Yangtze Daily serves the people of Wuhan by publishing essays that resonate with their experiences during the COVID-19 outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUBEI GOVERNMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Hubei Government is responsible for managing the COVID-19 outbreak in Wuhan, which directly impacts the city's response to the crisis. This government entity oversees the management of the coronavirus outbreak, coordinating public health responses and making critical decisions that affect the city. Through its efforts, the Hubei Government plays a crucial role in controlling the situation and ensuring the health and safety of the population in Wuhan.</data>
      <data key="d5">603d63bc59fd873441e2c2b5e86f64e6,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,e61ec0b2352248237abc9e924d1f0062</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PITTSBURGH&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Pittsburgh has sent medical supplies to Wuhan, demonstrating international solidarity during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HANKOU&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is a major city in China, and within it lies the district of Hankou. This indicates a geographical relationship between the two entities, with Hankou being a specific area within the larger urban framework of Wuhan.</data>
      <data key="d5">117c10f8d2ba000ee5b9e4627ab3dfb1,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </edge>
