      <data key="d5">c14142f937484ddfb159db76b5886c12</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;LEISHENSHAN HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Leishenshan Hospital is located in Wuhan and plays a crucial role in treating patients during the ongoing health crisis. It was specifically built to assist with the medical response to the outbreak, addressing the urgent medical needs of the community during this challenging time.</data>
      <data key="d5">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13,c7d14067bee9b74c3ed5d2f5b7f20d6e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;TONGJI HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Tongji Hospital is a key healthcare facility located in Wuhan, China. During the outbreak of the coronavirus, the hospital has played a significant role in managing non-coronavirus patients while also being involved in the reporting of coronavirus cases in the city. Wuhan serves as the backdrop for Tongji Hospital's operations, highlighting its importance in the local healthcare system amidst the ongoing health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d5">2442b273467e794640358f6408ecde1a,4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN UNION HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan Union Hospital is situated in Wuhan and plays a vital role in treating non-coronavirus patients amidst the health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;HUBEI PEOPLE&#8217;S HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Hubei People&#8217;s Hospital is based in Wuhan and is crucial for providing care to non-coronavirus patients during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;ROGUE VIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Rogue Virus, or novel coronavirus, is the primary health concern in Wuhan, leading to significant public health measures and responses."</data>
      <data key="d5">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PROVINCIAL LITERARY AND ARTS FEDERATION&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Provincial Literary and Arts Federation is a local organization based in Wuhan that has actively participated in the community's response to the crisis. It plays a significant role in community management during the outbreak, contributing to efforts aimed at addressing the challenges faced by the local population.</data>
      <data key="d5">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928,5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;WUCHANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuchang is also a district within Wuhan, establishing a geographical connection."</data>
      <data key="d5">5dce17a2098a6b5d363c295013eec01d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;NOVEL CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">4.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is the city where the Novel Coronavirus outbreak originated, making it the epicenter of the pandemic. The outbreak in Wuhan led to significant health and social challenges, directly impacting the city and its residents. As the initial site of the virus's spread, Wuhan's experiences are crucial for understanding the broader implications of the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d5">4da2d860213f5052c1d96ea58dbd19c5,68d1018c902661392b4e20435e4961ad,8119bda66f27343b4be177610dcff2af,f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;GOVERNMENT ORDER&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Government Order was issued in Wuhan to enforce strict quarantine measures during the Novel Coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;DOG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Dog provides companionship to the narrator during the quarantine in Wuhan, illustrating personal life amidst the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">f9bc05d223dec4b69bd57d94e14a6e1e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PEOPLE&#8217;S LIBERATION ARMY&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The People&#8217;s Liberation Army is involved in supporting Wuhan during the outbreak, indicating a direct relationship with the city."</data>
      <data key="d5">556bd422c25f731ed0b5aaf381face13</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE AUTHOR&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Author documents their experiences and observations in Wuhan during the outbreak, providing insights into the significant impact on daily life in the city. His literary contributions have earned him recognition and respect within the local community, indicating a strong reputation in Wuhan.</data>
      <data key="d5">13dcf66c4d2749898f0243f4429b9478,ecdbc80cd38edf6145de3f6de4c35bb9</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;PAN XIANGLI&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Pan Xiangli's promise of a meal together reflects the social connections and support among friends in Wuhan during the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">e5f23e41b03b71d778d0eeb5fcbec7c8</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE SU FAMILY&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Su Family is donating funds to support the people of Wuhan during the coronavirus outbreak, showing their concern for the city."</data>
      <data key="d5">630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">11.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan is recognized as the epicenter of the Coronavirus Outbreak, which originated in the city and subsequently led to a global pandemic. The outbreak has had profound effects on Wuhan, resulting in a public health crisis characterized by severe consequences and extensive restrictions. The city faced significant health and emotional challenges as it dealt with the initial and most severe impacts of the pandemic. In response to the crisis, urgent public health measures were implemented, and investigations were launched to understand the outbreak better. Additionally, the situation prompted notable community and volunteer efforts aimed at supporting the residents of Wuhan during this difficult time. As a critical location for understanding the pandemic's impact, Wuhan remains central to discussions surrounding the Coronavirus Outbreak and its ramifications.</data>
      <data key="d5">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a,11391ac84549db7d255187fbbc26b486,32eb98f2a79573ef66d4d36592a942ed,39d6ae4d79ba80953eb86122bce3240d,630fa90e9ff227f3fff1f91f6407fc27,70e8609ad54a494121d9ad67c2728482,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760,b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,c8e229d8fbd4f477126682d1b67e1bfd,db8aa816c2baf971734e93f0e59ddc26,f7d4aedaaebf83b5bb28320eecdc7d6c</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;ZHONGSHAN PARK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Zhongshan Park is a location within Wuhan, illustrating the impact of the pandemic on local public spaces."</data>
      <data key="d5">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;LIBERATION PARK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Liberation Park is another location in Wuhan affected by the pandemic, emphasizing the city's current state of emptiness."</data>
      <data key="d5">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;LAYAN ISLAND&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Layan Island is a destination for biking in Wuhan, indicating leisure activities impacted by the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">a5ef5074d98b2974239fc5ef79d3a408</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;XIANG XINRAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Xiang Xinran is a resident of Wuhan, directly experiencing the challenges posed by the coronavirus outbreak in the city."</data>
      <data key="d5">d493b79b718913aea1c87accaf09fc95</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;MR. LIU&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Mr. Liu plays a significant role in the context of Wuhan, where he sends fish to the narrator, symbolizing a connection of friendship and support that transcends geographical boundaries. Additionally, Mr. Liu's proposal for a quarantine model is pertinent to the ongoing crisis in Wuhan, which is currently experiencing a severe outbreak of coronavirus. This highlights Mr. Liu's involvement in addressing the challenges posed by the pandemic while also fostering personal relationships amidst the difficult circumstances.</data>
      <data key="d5">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d,b4fc820125edff1532326289b47fedb3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;TEMPORARY HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The construction of Temporary Hospitals in Wuhan is a direct response to the urgent need for medical facilities due to the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">0394c05194fa4023c0ff73ed7d00f80d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN CURSES&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan Curses reflect the frustrations of Wuhan residents during the coronavirus outbreak, highlighting social issues and public sentiment."</data>
      <data key="d5">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;GROUP-BUYING MODEL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Group-Buying Model has been utilized in Wuhan during the coronavirus outbreak, revealing logistical challenges faced by residents."</data>
      <data key="d5">5a40e5fe09f23ba1bb2dce7fe8777637</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;XIAO ZHOU&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Xiao Zhou manages the area in Wuhan, playing a role in community support during the Coronavirus Outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">107bf32484dae7a0e0c2c27dae44a96a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;BEIJING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Wuhan and Beijing are interconnected in the context of the outbreak that originated in Wuhan. Beijing serves as a significant point of communication regarding the crisis, indicating its role in managing the situation. However, the relationship between the two cities is strained, as evidenced by Beijing's refusal to allow individuals from Hubei, the province where Wuhan is located, to enter the city. This decision has direct implications for the residents of Wuhan, underscoring the ongoing challenges they face during the outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d5">941fd97efac4d3db43e927529ff925c4,a5f44583790812ccdd6501f16f17d3f7</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;NATIONAL EMERGENCY RESPONSE NETWORK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan is the city where the National Emergency Response Network is proposed to be implemented to manage the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">f0d559329d874e435f04be915b85b185</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;VEGETABLE DONATIONS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan is experiencing issues with the distribution of Vegetable Donations, highlighting the logistical challenges during the pandemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">3b5ca06477ea6649725a16d09d87927a</data>
    </edge>
