      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Help Hotline was established to assist those stuck in Wuhan during the quarantine, indicating a response to the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">3d6a788010fe75ade47b4927dc7a6c2c</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;FANG FANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Fang Fang is a writer who documents her experiences and observations in her diary, which is set in Wuhan, the epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak. Through her writings, she captures the lives and characteristics of the people of Wuhan, showcasing her deep connection to the city during this challenging time. Her diary serves as a poignant reflection of the struggles and resilience of the community amidst the pandemic.</data>
      <data key="d5">22ab7ca013baeeffead27cc8cbcbae9f,4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3,9218d4cc654424beaa3f2f897af0e760</data>
    </edge>
