      <data key="d5">16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;DR. WANG GUANGFA&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Dr. Wang Guangfa's experience with the virus is significant to the context of the outbreak in Wuhan. His statements during the outbreak had a direct impact on the residents of Wuhan, influencing public perception and response to the virus. As a key figure in the early stages of the outbreak, Dr. Wang's insights and communications played a crucial role in shaping how the community understood and reacted to the emerging health crisis.</data>
      <data key="d5">b15e3136b1d250627e50da850c2559c5,b311864054a222e4315c575af55fca03</data>
    </edge>
