    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN&quot;" target="&quot;ER XIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Er Xiang plays a crucial role in supporting the narrator by helping them share their diary entries on WeChat, highlighting a strong and supportive relationship during a challenging period. Her communication efforts are particularly significant in the context of the outbreak in Wuhan, as she strives to convey important messages related to the situation there. This indicates that Er Xiang is not only a source of emotional support but also actively engaged in addressing the challenges posed by the circumstances in Wuhan.</data>
      <data key="d5">7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,8475b5acce1676914c613935d50901d6</data>
    </edge>
