    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;HAN DONG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Han Dong's experience of being stuck in Hubei during the lockdown highlights the personal struggles faced by individuals in the province during the pandemic. His situation serves as a poignant example of the challenges and hardships that many people encountered while navigating the restrictions and uncertainties imposed by the lockdown in Hubei.</data>
      <data key="d5">24f82cd50519ba6e59f128ccf5c821f6,9d9621a0d3abed625eaaf2428ed7b0bb</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;JANUARY 14 MEETING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Officials from Hubei participated in the January 14 Meeting, indicating their involvement in the response to the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">88c0aa6bc6e9484db48221e353dd96ab</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Hubei is the province most affected by The Coronavirus, leading to significant public health and economic challenges for its residents."</data>
      <data key="d5">26fd52ba788ccd2a6e5404977738bfda</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;SHANCHUN COUNTY&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Shanchun County is part of Hubei province, and both locations are experiencing the aftermath of the quarantine."</data>
      <data key="d5">70a8fc915dd17756704d7e08d2139eaa</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;DR. ZHANG WENHONG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Zhang's guidance is relevant to the people of Hubei, who are dealing with the aftermath of the outbreak and its societal impacts."</data>
      <data key="d5">82a05824c63b582fce46f3e7719ac6b6</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;HUBEI&quot;" target="&quot;BEIJING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Beijing's policies of exclusion directly affect the residents of Hubei, highlighting a geographical and political relationship during a health crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">5723f9f649f81825f888c51d24c2d1a5</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WUHAN INSTITUTE OF VIROLOGY&quot;" target="&quot;THE VIRAL OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">128.0</data>
