    <edge source="&quot;COVID-19&quot;" target="&quot;THE VIRAL OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">128.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"COVID-19 is the disease that characterized the viral outbreak, leading to widespread health and social impacts in Wuhan and beyond."</data>
