    <edge source="&quot;HUAZHONG UNIVERSITY OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY&quot;" target="&quot;TONGJI HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">129.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Huazhong University of Science and Technology is affiliated with Tongji Hospital, highlighting a significant relationship between the two entities. This affiliation plays a crucial role in enhancing the medical education and research efforts at both the university and the hospital. Tongji Hospital, in turn, is connected to Huazhong University of Science and Technology, further emphasizing the collaborative nature of their relationship. Together, they work towards advancing healthcare education and research initiatives.</data>
