      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Duan Zhengcheng was a professor at Huazhong University of Science and Technology, indicating his affiliation with the institution and the impact of his loss on the university."</data>
      <data key="d5">4c6ae1a529eeabbb8b203fca0dffe928</data>
