    <edge source="&quot;THE OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;FANG FANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Fang Fang's diary offers a personal perspective on her experiences during "The Outbreak," a pandemic that significantly impacted her life and the lives of those around her. The diary not only chronicles her thoughts and feelings during this challenging time but also highlights the broader societal implications of the outbreak. Additionally, Fang Fang's name has become associated with a controversial book related to the outbreak, which has influenced the narrator's reputation. This connection underscores the complex interplay between personal narratives and public perception during a crisis.</data>
      <data key="d5">203baa1288c7f64829148f9e461d93b8,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </edge>
