      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Traditional Chinese medicine has gained recognition for its effectiveness during the coronavirus outbreak, indicating a relationship based on treatment methods."</data>
      <data key="d5">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;DOCTOR FRIEND&quot;">
      <data key="d3">3.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The "Doctor Friend" offers essential insights and perspectives regarding the "Coronavirus Outbreak," emphasizing the implications of the outbreak and the conditions within hospitals. This relationship is characterized by a foundation of medical expertise and information sharing, as the Doctor Friend provides professional insights into the realities of the outbreak and the management of patients affected by it. Through these contributions, the Doctor Friend plays a significant role in enhancing understanding of the challenges posed by the Coronavirus Outbreak.</data>
      <data key="d5">2a8c8258f10a9f09d9652df720f77449,7e514e9368f9e3a515f69f27af26eab4,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;TEMPORARY HOSPITALS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The "CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK" led to the establishment of "TEMPORARY HOSPITALS" as a critical response to manage patient care during the crisis. These temporary hospitals were specifically created to address the surge of COVID-19 cases, particularly noted during the outbreak in Wuhan. Their primary purpose was to provide additional healthcare capacity and support for the increasing number of patients affected by the virus.</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,a258c0fe44c182e59b2af3913158bbf1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;TIAN HAN THEATER&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The concert at Tian Han Theater contributed to the spread of the coronavirus, resulting in fatalities among the cinematographers present."</data>
      <data key="d5">73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN HEALTH COMMISSION&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Wuhan Health Commission is directly involved in managing the coronavirus outbreak, influencing public health responses in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d5">973c13961f84e95436b515301155082a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;FANG FANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Fang Fang reflects on the effects of the coronavirus outbreak in her writings, particularly regarding the people of Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d5">4a02f8de11375d220370828d6659eaf3</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;" target="&quot;CENSORSHIP&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
