      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Government is actively responding to the challenges posed by the coronavirus outbreak that originated in Wuhan. It is responsible for implementing various measures aimed at controlling the spread of the coronavirus, including the establishment of quarantine protocols in Hubei. These actions reflect the Government's commitment to managing the public health crisis effectively.</data>
