    <edge source="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS&quot;" target="&quot;THE EPIDEMIC&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Coronavirus has led to a significant epidemic that has profoundly impacted many lives. This epidemic is characterized by widespread health and emotional challenges, particularly evident in Wuhan and extending beyond its borders. As a direct consequence of the Coronavirus outbreak, extensive health measures have been implemented to address the crisis and mitigate its effects on the population.</data>
