    <edge source="&quot;DR. LI WENLIANG&quot;" target="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Dr. Li Wenliang was an ophthalmologist at Central Hospital who tragically died during the outbreak, becoming a symbol of the significant challenges faced by medical staff during this crisis. His case is closely associated with the events at Central Hospital, where numerous deaths occurred, leading to investigations and heightened public scrutiny regarding the handling of the situation.</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,16a55ea42b0f86d2dc184c5e8348f4d3</data>
    </edge>
