    <edge source="&quot;CORONAVIRUS&quot;" target="&quot;XI-WEN CHOIR&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Xi-Wen Choir, as a local arts group, is part of the cultural landscape affected by the coronavirus pandemic in Wuhan."</data>
      <data key="d5">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;LI WENLIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Li Wenliang was a doctor at Central Hospital who gained significant attention during the coronavirus outbreak. He faced censure for his early warnings about the virus, which underscored important issues of accountability within the healthcare system. His actions and the subsequent response from authorities made him a notable figure during this critical time, highlighting the challenges faced by medical professionals in communicating urgent health information.</data>
      <data key="d5">0f6f81b9c147f34def6ae3e90cdc4a8d,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS EPIDEMIC&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Central Hospital is at the forefront of the response to the Coronavirus Epidemic, treating many patients and facing overwhelming challenges."</data>
      <data key="d5">81ac5d9d3486351095e7556baea13868</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. MEI ZHONGMING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Mei Zhongming worked at Central Hospital and was significantly impacted by the challenges posed by the Coronavirus Epidemic."</data>
      <data key="d5">81ac5d9d3486351095e7556baea13868</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. MEI&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Mei was a doctor associated with Central Hospital, and his death has impacted the community and the hospital's staff."</data>
      <data key="d5">75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;WUHAN SECOND HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wuhan Second Hospital was previously connected to Central Hospital, indicating a historical relationship between the two organizations."</data>
      <data key="d5">75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;CHUTIAN NEW MEDIA&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Chutian New Media reported on the conditions at Central Hospital during the coronavirus outbreak, providing critical information to the public."</data>
      <data key="d5">75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;THE CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Central Hospital has been significantly affected by the Coronavirus Outbreak, serving as a frontline facility for treatment. It plays a crucial role in the response to the outbreak, where many medical professionals, including Ai Fen and Dr. Jiang, are actively involved in providing care and managing the crisis.</data>
      <data key="d5">3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa,75ac580f4988934d2ae2bfcfe1d611b4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;LI LIANG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Li Liang was treated at Central Hospital, indicating a direct connection between his health issues and the medical facility."</data>
      <data key="d5">05facbc17efc22acf453283e5f155f6b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. ZHU HEPING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Zhu Heping was a physician at Central Hospital who died during the coronavirus outbreak, highlighting the hospital's struggles."</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. JIANG XUEQING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Dr. Jiang Xueqing was a physician and the Director of a department at Central Hospital. His passing has significantly impacted the hospital community, particularly during the outbreak, highlighting the profound losses experienced by the institution.</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f,3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;MEI ZHONGMING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Mei Zhongming was the Director of the Department of Ophthalmology at Central Hospital who passed away during the outbreak, reflecting the hospital's difficulties."</data>
      <data key="d5">0ca36acc21e63cef3f8f8b702b23a30f</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. YUEN KWOK-YUNG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Yuen Kwok-Yung's interview reflects on the operations of Central Hospital and the need for better management during the coronavirus outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">73f0409eddb363c0d94171d352c28474</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;AI FEN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Ai Fen is a physician working at Central Hospital, where she has been involved in the response to the outbreak."</data>
      <data key="d5">3e8474bb1550779641628567633011fa</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;DR. YANG FAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Dr. Yang Fan is a frontline doctor at Central Hospital, highlighting the hospital's role in the healthcare crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;WANG PING&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Wang Ping is an Assistant Director at Central Hospital, indicating his significant position within the organization during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d5">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;LIU LI&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Liu Li was a member of the Medical Ethics Committee at Central Hospital, where she played a significant role in addressing the hospital's ethical considerations during a crisis. Her involvement in the committee highlights the hospital's commitment to navigating complex ethical dilemmas, particularly during challenging times. Tragically, Liu Li's death serves as a poignant reminder of the struggles faced by Central Hospital during the pandemic, emphasizing the profound impact of the crisis on its staff and operations.</data>
      <data key="d5">a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044,a65c4ed02bcde76982703679e0df66df</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;YI FAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Yi Fan is the Assistant Director of the Thoracic Surgery Department at Central Hospital. In this role, he plays a crucial part in the medical team, particularly during times of crisis, highlighting his importance within the hospital's operations and patient care.</data>
      <data key="d5">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;HU WEIFENG&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Hu Weifeng is employed at Central Hospital, where he serves as the Assistant Director of the Department of Urology. In this critical role, he has been instrumental in the organization, particularly during health crises, highlighting his importance within the hospital's operations.</data>
      <data key="d5">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d,a47098bdb1e8c07bb54ff29a75698044</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;SINO-JAPANESE FRIENDSHIP HOSPITAL&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Both hospitals are mentioned in the context of miraculous recoveries during a health crisis, indicating their significance in the community."</data>
      <data key="d5">477b841f2c30a02cbf570056bfcf7a3d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;CENTRAL HOSPITAL&quot;" target="&quot;MEDICAL ETHICS COMMITTEE MEMBER LIU LI&quot;">
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
