      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Li Wenliang's legacy is honored through the proposed Wailing Web, which aims to provide a space for collective mourning and remembrance."</data>
      <data key="d5">f7d4aedaaebf83b5bb28320eecdc7d6c</data>
    </edge>
