      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">The Hubei Daily News and Media Group and the Yangtze Daily Newspaper Group are both significant players in the news landscape of Wuhan and Hubei Province. They provide extensive coverage of local events and issues, contributing to the region's media environment. As major media organizations, they likely compete for readership and influence in their reporting of news, highlighting their importance in shaping public discourse within the province.</data>
