    <edge source="&quot;MR. LI&quot;" target="&quot;SU HUAJIAN&quot;">
      <data key="d3">2.0</data>
      <data key="d4">Mr. Li and Su Huajian were close members of the Xi-Wen Choir, where their friendship was marked by shared experiences and mutual support. Mr. Li expressed concern over Su Huajian's sudden absence, highlighting the significance of their bond within the choir. Additionally, Mr. Li's essay honors Su Huajian, further indicating the depth of their friendship and the impact Su had on his life.</data>
      <data key="d5">6061aecaff4e505cf2d885fa814994e6,db3e66e7b4d19ca23e8d685bcc43901c</data>
